7-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ESouth%20of%20England%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20I%20was%20into%20soccer%20and%20skateboarding%2C%20and%20my%20other%20career%20goal%20was%20to%20be%20a%20skateboard%20film%20maker.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20sister%20was%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnorland-nannies-what-a-day-looks-2021-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Enanny%20in%20Norland%20College%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20and%20I%20saw%20how%20much%20she%20loved%20her%20studies.%20She%20got%20to%20do%20incredible%20things%2C%20and%20she%20was%20always%20telling%20me%20about%20the%20fun%20she%20had%20at%20work.%20I%20knew%20the%20job%20would%20be%20perfect%20for%20me.%20I'm%20the%20nice%20guy%2C%20who%20thrives%20on%20making%20other%20people%20happy.%20My%20three%20sisters%20and%20I%20were%20all%20adopted%2C%20so%20I%20grew%20up%20knowing%20that%20caring%20isn't%20about%20a%20blood%20connection.%20It's%20a%20choice%2C%20and%20I%20wanted%20to%20choose%20to%20care%20for%20children.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20was%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fuk-nannies-elite-training-self-defense-childcare-norland-college-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehard%20work%20to%20get%20into%20Norland%20College%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20I%20had%20to%20redo%20some%20of%20my%20high%20school%20classes%20because%20my%20grades%20weren't%20high%20enough.%20Luckily%2C%20everyone%20from%20my%20friends%20and%20family%20to%20school%20counselors%20supported%20me.%20I%20think%20they%20could%20see%20how%20nannying%20was%20a%20perfect%20fit%20for%20my%20personality.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e0564e9a-df84-464f-8e43-d515dbcc3195%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20felt%20so%20awkward%20the%20first%20time%20I%20held%20an%20infant%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20I%20was%20finally%20%3C