has%20become%20the%20%26quot%3BIt%26quot%3B%20girl%20of%20the%20fashion%20industry.%20It's%20number%20two%20on%20The%20Lyst%20Fashion%20Index%2C%20a%20quarterly%20measure%20of%20the%20hottest%20fashion%20brands.%20Searches%20for%20Miu%20Miu%20are%20up%2047%25%20this%20year%20on%20luxury%20resale%20platform%20The%20RealReal.%20The%20micro%20minis%20that%20stormed%20the%20runway%20in%202021%2C%20a%20sneaker%20collab%20with%20New%20Balance%2C%20and%20the%20quilted%20Wander%20bags%20have%20become%20must-have%20looks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20translated%20into%20impressive%20results%3A%20Retail%20sales%20were%20up%2050%25%20in%202023%20and%2086%25%20in%20the%20first%20half%20of%20this%20year.%20Last%20quarter%2C%20website%20traffic%20was%20up%20110%25%20year%20over%20year%2C%20Stifel's%20Rogerio%20Fujimori%20reported%20in%20his%20July%20note.%20The%20brand%20will%20likely%20hit%20%241%20billion%20in%20revenue%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224663%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Miu%20Miu%20micro%20miniskirt%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66f6fa7e75c877a99b616284%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223109%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMiu%20Miu's%20micro%20miniskirts%20became%20a%20must-have%20look%20for%20the%20fashion%20set.%3Cp%3EEdward%20Berthelot%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EPart%20of%20it%20is%20the%20brand's%20messaging.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMiu%20Miu%20is%20resonating%20with%20consumers%20because%20of%20a%20savvy%20mix%20of%20product%20and%20communication%20marketing%2C%26quot%3B%20Solca%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20recent%20note%2C%20he%20highlighted%20the%20brand's%20events%20%E2%80%94%20a%20tennis%20club%2C%20literary%20club%2C%20and%20film%20series%20%E2%80%94%20that%20go%20beyond%20just%20fashion%20to%20form%20a%20%26quot%3Bcultural%20aesthetic.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMiu%20Miu%20has%20embraced%20stars%20(Sydney%20Sweeney%20and%20Gigi%20Hadid%20were%20featured%20in%20recent%20campaigns)%2C%20which%20has%20energized%20its%20following.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20brand%20has%20also%20managed%20to%20tap%20into%20Asian%20markets%20%E2%80%94%20one%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-luxury-retail-sales-slowdown-brands-fashion-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emost%20challenging%20sectors%20for%20luxury%20brands%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAgain%2C%20some%20smart%20marketing%20has%20helped.%20The%20brand%20enlisted%20K-pop%20icons%20as%20ambassadors%20and%20dressed%20Chinese%20stars%20Lexie%20Liu%2C%20Zhao%20Jinmai%2C%20and%20Wu%20Yanshu.%20It%20also%20increased%20spending%20on%20Little%20Red%20Book%2C%20a%20social%20media%20platform%20in%20China%2C%20and%20threw%20events%20in%20Tokyo%2C%20Taipei%2C%20and%20Nanjing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20short%20%E2%80%94%20pun%20intended%20%E2%80%94%20you%20can't%20get%20trendier%20than%20Miu%20Miu%20right%20now%2C%20and%20being%20trendy%20is%20good%20for%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229c90104e-4760-4af7-8e30-9a1c1dfe68ef%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20business%20behind%20the%20boom%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Miu%20Miu's%20popularity%2C%20as%20attention-grabbing%20as%20it%20is%2C%20is%20only%20part%20of%20the%20story.%20The%20brand%20accounted%20for%2015%25%20of%20Prada's%20sales%20last%20year.%20HSBC%20analysts%20called%20its%20growth%20a%20%26quot%3B(big)%20cherry%20on%20the%20cake%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20the%20cake%20being%20Prada%20(which%20didn't%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider%20for%20this%20story).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBehind%20Miu%20Miu's%20Mary%20Jane%20shoes%20and%20Arcade%20bags%20is%20a%20success%20story%20at%20its%20parent%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20group's%20namesake%20line%20is%20growing%2C%20albeit%20at%20a%20slower%20and%20steadier%20pace.%20Prada's%20retail%20sales%20were%20up%203%25%20in%20the%20first%20half%20of%20the%20year%20compared%20to%20last%20year%20and%207%25%20in%202023.%20It's%20been%20among%20Lyst's%20top%20five%20hottest%20brands%20since%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20didn't%20happen%20by%20accident%3A%20In%202017%2C%20Prada%20committed%20to%20a%20turnaround%20strategy%20following%20a%20few%20losing%20years%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eand%20a%20drop%20in%20profitability.%20At%20more%20than%20100%20years%20old%2C%20Prada%20hadn't%20entered%20the%20new%20millennium%3A%20Its%20full%20product%20line%20wasn't%20available%20through%20e-commerce%2C%20and%20its%20advertising%20wasn't%20digitized.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%202015%2C%20the%20tide%20really%20turned%20for%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Jelena%20Sokolova%2C%20a%20senior%20analyst%20for%20Morningstar%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BThey%20fared%20worse%20than%20the%20industry%3A%20Sales%20were%20negative%20for%20a%20number%20of%20years%3B%20their%20earnings%20plummeted.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20response%2C%20Prada%20focused%20on%20retail%2C%20a%20channel%20in%20which%20it%20can%20control%20prices%20and%20cut%20back%20on%20wholesale%2C%20which%20now%20represents%20only%2011%25%20of%20sales.%20It%20made%20an%20effort%20to%20cut%20down%20on%20discounts%20%E2%80%94%20a%20problem%20that%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-burberry-became-fashions-biggest-fail-stock-drop-ceo-ousting-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplagued%20labels%20like%20Burberry%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Gucci%20and%20can%20lead%20to%20diminishing%20brand%20perception.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20its%20retail%20stores%2C%20new%20CEO%20Andrea%20Guerra%2C%20who%20arrived%20in%202023%20from%20LVMH%2C%20has%20drilled%20down%20on%20productivity%2C%20or%20how%20much%20money%20each%20square%20foot%20of%20retail%20space%20generates%2C%20by%20launching%20in-store%20installations%2C%20forming%20one-to-one%20relationships%20between%20sales%20associates%20and%20customers%2C%20and%20infusing%20stores%20with%20wearable%20pieces%20and%20collaborations.%20The%20company%20closed%20stores%20that%20weren't%20performing%20and%20renovated%20the%20ones%20that%20were.%20It's%20worked%3A%20Retail%20productivity%20has%20increased%2032.5%25%20between%202019%20and%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Prada%20store%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66f6fb0df9f6733e4be06ca1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPrada%20has%20invested%20in%20its%20retail%20locations%2C%20like%20this%20one%20in%20Hong%20Kong%2C%20to%20maximize%20sales%20per%20square%20foot.%3Cp%3ESOPA%20Images%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20has%20also%20been%20a%20slew%20of%20management%20changes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202020%2C%20the%20company%20brought%20on%20Raf%20Simons%2C%20heralded%20as%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20stars%20in%20the%20design%20world%2C%20as%20co-creative%20director%2C%20sharing%20the%20title%20with%20Muccia%20Prada%20%E2%80%94%20the%20company's%20billionaire%20heiress%20who%20The%20New%20York%20Times%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2023%2F10%2F04%2Fstyle%2Fmiu-miu-chanel-louis-vuitton-paris-fashion-week.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereferred%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20as%20%26quot%3Bthe%20most%20influential%20woman%20in%20fashion.%26quot%3B%20Prada%20now%20has%20more%20time%20to%20use%20her%20keen%20sense%20of%20design%20at%20Miu%20Miu.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20years%20following%2C%20it%20recruited%20talent%20from%20LVMH%20and%20Goldman%20Sachs%20to%20join%20its%20top%20ranks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20then%20there%20is%20the%20sheer%20cyclicality%20of%20fashion%20and%20the%20fact%20that%2C%20after%20a%20few%20years%20of%20being%20less-than-hot%2C%20Prada%20is%20once%20again%20on%20the%20rise.%20It%20has%20embraced%20the%201990s%20and%20Y2K%20aesthetic%20%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%94%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ea%20heyday%20for%20Prada%20%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%94%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Epopular%20with%20Gen%20Z%20and%20was%20the%20most%20searched%20brand%20among%20the%20demographic%20on%20The%20RealReal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHit%20products%20pushed%20the%20profitable%20leather%20goods%20category%20to%20revenues%20of%20more%20than%20%242%20billion%20last%20year.%20There%20was%20a%20reimagining%20of%20the%20early%202010s%20it-bag%2C%20the%20Galleria%2C%20complete%20with%20a%20Scarlett%20Johansson-led%20campaign.%20Other%20handbag%20rereleases%2C%20like%20that%20of%20the%20Nylon%2C%20have%20taken%20off%2C%20while%20new%20purse%20styles%20like%20the%20Buckle%20and%20Arqu%C3%A9%20got%20callouts%20in%20last%20year's%20earnings%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20momentum%20gave%20the%20brand%20an%20upper%20hand%20going%20into%20the%20luxury%20downturn.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20prioritize%20which%20brands%20they%20want%20to%20spend%20on.%20With%20a%20limited%20budget%2C%20first%2C%20you%20drop%20the%20ones%20that%20were%20not%20hot%20to%20begin%20with%2C%26quot%3B%20Sokolova%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221cb26ff7-f524-43b6-b92f-40ccaa4587ca%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ECan%20Prada's%20hot%20streak%20last%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EJust%20as%20fashion%20comes%20in%2C%20it%20can%20come%20out.%20And%20Prada's%20story%20%E2%80%94%20particularly%20Miu%20Miu's%20rapid-fire%20growth%20%E2%80%94%20in%20some%20ways%20mimics%20that%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgucci-sales-profit-reputation-falling-luxury-kering-michele-china-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGucci's%20hype-driven%20rise%20and%20plummeting%20fall%20under%20Alessandro%20Michele%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20kind%20of%20become%20a%20victim%20of%20your%20own%20success%2C%26quot%3B%20Sokolova%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20Prada%20and%20Miu%20Miu%20are%20susceptible%20to%20volatility%2C%20though%20for%20different%20reasons.%20Miu%20Miu%20is%20still%20relatively%20small%2C%20meaning%20its%20brand%20identity%20is%20not%20yet%20established%20enough%20to%20withstand%20the%20whims%20of%20consumers.%20CEO%20Guerra%20has%20acknowledged%20that%20such%20incredible%20growth%20can%20lead%20to%20a%20challenge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20appears%20to%20be%20a%20glass%20ceiling%2C%26quot%3B%20Solca%20wrote%20in%20a%20recent%20note.%20%26quot%3BBeing%20prominent%20brings%20fatigue%3A%20after%20a%20while%2C%20consumers%20feel%20they%20have%20seen%20and%20done%20enough%20with%20these%20brands%20and%20move%20on.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPrada%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20is%20more%20exposed%20in%20the%20cyclical%20ready-to-wear%20category%20%E2%80%94%20which%20makes%20up%2032%25%20of%20sales%20%E2%80%94%20than%20other%20brands%20like%20Gucci%20and%20YSL.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20there%20are%20signs%20of%20continued%20growth%3A%20Miu%20Miu%20is%20adding%2010%20to%2015%20stores%20next%20year%2C%20while%20Prada%20is%20adding%20five%20to%2010%2C%20the%20company%20has%20said.%20The%20brand's%20retail%20footprint%20is%20particularly%20underpenetrated%20in%20the%20US.%20The%20company's%20beauty%20business%20is%20still%20nascent.%20Last%20year%2C%20it%20launched%20skincare%20and%20makeup%20through%20a%20partnership%20with%20L'Or%C3%A9al%2C%20and%20there%20is%20more%20money%20to%20be%20made%20in%20that%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20so%20much%20control%20of%20its%20sales%20chain%2C%20the%20company%20can%20raise%20prices%20and%20limit%20overexposure%20through%20low-end%20collaborations%20or%20expansion%20into%20cheap%20categories.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlus%2C%20the%20slowdown%20hasn't%20happened%20yet%3A%20Miu%20Miu%20website%20traffic%20and%20sales%20continued%20to%20grow%20between%20the%20first%20and%20second%20quarters%2C%20and%20the%20company%20maintains%20it's%20not%20a%20flash%20in%20the%20pan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20result%20of%20many%20years%20of%20work%20on%20the%20brand%2C%20on%20the%20products%2C%20on%20the%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20Guerra%20said%20about%20Miu%20Miu's%20success%20on%20the%20company's%20most%2