%20Van%20de%20Plassche%20had%20been%20on%20the%20personal%20development%20treadmill%20for%20years%20before%20she%20tried%20microdosing.%3Cp%3EPeggy%20Van%20de%20Plassche%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EPeggy%20Van%20de%20Plassche%20felt%20depressed%20and%20anxious%20until%20she%20started%20microdosing%20psilocybin%20three%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-microdosing-2019-1%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMicrodosing%20%3C%2Fa%3Etiny%20amounts%20of%20psychedelics%20has%20gained%20interest%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20but%20is%20illegal%20under%20U.S.%20federal%20law.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThere's%20not%20enough%20evidence%20to%20prove%20that%20it%20works%20yet%2C%20and%20data%20is%20mostly%20self-reported.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Peggy%20Van%20de%20Plassche%2C%2047%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20The%20Microdose%20Diet%2C%20who%20lives%20in%20Toronto.%20The%20following%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUntil%20a%20few%20years%20ago%2C%20I%20had%20been%20working%20in%20finance%20for%2020%20years.%20I%20liked%20the%20industry%2C%20but%20I%20felt%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffounder-mental-health-crisis-startups-venture-capital-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econstantly%20anxious%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20emotionally%20numb%2C%20and%20depressed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20didn't%20feel%20like%20the%20time%20I%20was%20putting%20in%20and%20the%20value%20I%20was%20bringing%20to%20the%20business%20where%20I%20worked%20were%20being%20recognized.%20I%20was%20on%20high%20alert%20all%20the%20time%2C%20responding%20to%20emails%20from%20the%20moment%20I%20opened%20my%20eyes%20in%20the%20morning%20until%20my%20head%20hit%20the%20pillow%20at%20night.%20My%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-deal-with-stress-burnout-work-mental-health-professional-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estress%20levels%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20so%20constant%20that%20there%20was%20no%20space%20for%20joyful%20feelings.%20When%20I%20got%20a%20promotion%2C%20for%20example%2C%20I%20wouldn't%20feel%20excited%2C%20even%20though%20I'd%20been%20working%20toward%20it%20for%20a%20long%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-happy-job-hopping-quit-without-backup-oliver-wyman-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ejob-hopped%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20lot%20because%20I%20would%20eventually%20become%20frustrated%20by%20something%2C%20a%20difficult%20relationship%2C%20or%20a%20project%20that%20was%20not%20going%20at%20the%20speed%20I%20wanted%2C%20and%20I'd%20leave.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%2C%20I%20blamed%20external%20factors%20for%20how%20I%20was%20feeling%2C%20but%20each%20time%20I%20switched%20jobs%2C%20after%20six%20months%20or%20so%2C%20mentally%2C%20I'd%20be%20in%20the%20exact%20same%20place%20as%20before.%20In%20hindsight%2C%20I%20realized%20that%20when%20you're%20unhappy%20with%20yourself%2C%20you%20can%20change%20your%20environment%20as%20much%20as%20you%20like%2C%20but%20you'll%20have%20the%20same%20problem%20if%20you%20haven't%20changed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20COVID%20came%20around%2C%20I%20had%20my%20own%20consulting%20company%20and%20I%20was%20advising%20pension%20and%20VC%20funds%20on%20investments%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmost-promising-financial-startups-fintechs-2023%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFinTech%20space%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Business%20had%20really%20slowed%20in%20that%20period%2C%20which%20meant%20I%20had%20more%20time%20to%20think%2C%20and%20it%20really%20became%20apparent%20that%20I%20had%20a%20lot%20of%20anxiety%20and%20depression.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20been%20on%20the%20personal%20development%20treadmill%20for%20quite%20some%20time%20already.%20I%20had%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsigns-to-quit-your-therapist-or-therapy-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20tried%20therapy%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20many%20other%20techniques%20and%20had%20seen%20some%20improvement%20but%20I%20only%20felt%20about%205%25%20better%20after%2012%20years%2C%20which%20just%20wasn't%20enough.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAround%20that%20time%20I%20started%20to%20notice%20articles%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrodose-magic-mushrooms-increase-productivity-at-work-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emicrodosing%20psychedelics%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20manage%20stress%20and%20anxiety%20and%20boost%20focus%20popping%20up%20in%20the%20business%20publications%20I%20was%20reading.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20read%20one%20article%2C%20then%20two%2C%20then%20three%2C%20and%20I%20was%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat's%20going%20on%20here%3F%26quot%3B%20In%20my%20mind%2C%20you're%20taking%20psychedelics%20to%20go%20to%20a%20rave.%20You're%20taking%20three%20grams%2C%20and%20you're%20dancing!%20I%20wanted%20to%20know%20more%2C%20so%20I%20turned%20to%20clinical%20studies%20and%20really%20did%20some%20research.%20I%20discovered%20that%20the%20FDA%20had%20classified%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdepression-magic-mushrooms-ingredient-psilocybin-hallucinate-symptoms-improve-risks-2022-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epsilocybin%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20a%20breakthrough%20therapy%20for%20resistant%20depression%20in%202018.%20It%20looked%20really%20promising.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20close%20to%20breaking%20point%20and%20simply%20couldn't%20take%20the%20constant%20negativity%20in%20my%20head%20anymore.%20So%20I%20decided%20to%20try%20micro-dosing%20psilocybin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Peggy%20Van%20de%20Plasscha%20stands%20on%20a%20stage%2C%20holding%20a%20microphone.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20s