%20have%20largely%20steered%20clear%20of%20the%20presidential%20race%2C%20but%20both%20candidates%20have%20taken%20notice%20of%20crypto's%20influence.%20Former%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20has%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-bitcoin-stance-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecourting%20crypto-focused%20voters%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-crypto-partners-chase-herro-zachary-folkman-lawsuits-jail-debt-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etrying%20to%20launch%20some%20sort%20of%20digital-asset%20venture%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20his%20own.%20Vice%20President%20Kamala%20Harris%20is%20paying%20lip%20service%20to%20crypto%2C%20too.%20If%20you%20can't%20beat%20the%20crypto%20bros%2C%20join%20'em%2C%20or%20at%20least%20give%20them%20a%20wink%20and%20a%20nod.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20and%20Harris%20have%20different%20reasons%20to%20try%20to%20attract%20the%20crypto%20community%20%E2%80%94%20donors%2C%20voters%2C%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20former%20president%20likes%20anyone%20who%20flatters%20him%2C%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20some%20extent%2C%20it's%20a%20%26quot%3Bmight%20as%20well%26quot%3B-type%20situation.%20Except%20for%20the%20people%20who%20%3Cem%3Ereally%20%3C%2Fem%3Ecare%20about%20crypto%2C%20nobody%20actually%20cares%20about%20crypto%2C%20so%20being%20nice%20about%20it%20is%20basically%20free.%20And%20in%20a%20race%20with%20a%20razor-thin%20margin%2C%20everything%20counts%20%E2%80%94%20including%2C%20maybe%2C%20the%20vote%20of%20some%20dogecoin-loving%20guy%20in%20a%20crucial%20Wisconsin%20county%20or%20an%20extra%20few%20thousand%20dollars%20from%20a%20tech%20donor%20who%20had%20been%20sitting%20on%20the%20sidelines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20not%20always%20been%20a%20fan%20of%20crypto.%20Back%20in%202021%2C%20he%20said%20it%20seemed%20like%20a%20scam%20and%20described%20it%20as%20a%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foxbusiness.com%2Fpolitics%2Fcrypto-potentially-a-disaster-waiting-to-happen-trump%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edisaster%20waiting%20to%20happen%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%20On%20the%202024%20campaign%20trail%2C%20however%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump-going-for-crypto-bro-vote-world-liberty-financial-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETrump%20has%20been%20happy%20to%20embrace%20the%20community%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20summer%20he%20appeared%20at%20a%20bitcoin%20conference%20in%20Nashville%2C%20where%20he%20vowed%20to%20make%20the%20United%20States%20the%20%26quot%3Bcrypto%20capital%20of%20the%20planet%26quot%3B%20and%20told%20the%20audience%20to%20%26quot%3Bhave%20fun%26quot%3B%20with%20their%20bitcoin%20and%20the%20other%20things%20they%20were%20playing%20with.%20He%20also%20attended%20an%20accompanying%20fundraiser%2C%20where%20tickets%20maxed%20out%20at%20%24844%2C600.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBig%20names%20in%20the%20arena%2C%20such%20as%20Marc%20Andreessen%20and%20Ben%20Horowitz%20of%20Andreessen%20Horowitz%20and%20Cameron%20and%20Tyler%20Winklevoss%20of%20Gemini%20and%20Facebook%20fame%2C%20have%20thrown%20their%20support%20behind%20Trump.%20He's%20made%20all%20sorts%20of%20promises%20about%20crypto%2C%20including%20that%20he'd%20create%20a%20%26quot%3Bstrategic%20national%20bitcoin%20stockpile%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20under%20his%20watch%2C%20crypto%20rules%20would%20be%20written%20by%20people%20who%20%26quot%3Blove%26quot%3B%20the%20industry%20rather%20than%20%26quot%3Bhate%26quot%3B%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20why%20the%20flip-flop%3F%20For%20one%20thing%2C%20crypto%20is%20sort%20of%20a%20natural%20fit%20for%20Trump.%20It%20has%20a%20libertarian%20and%20freedom-focused%20bent%20that%20aligns%20more%20naturally%20with%20the%20GOP%2C%20even%20though%20Trump%20is%20far%20from%20a%20libertarian.%20Its%20fans%2Fusers%2Finvestors%20are%20disproportionately%20young%20men%2C%20a%20constituency%20whose%20vote%20the%20Republican%20nominee%20is%20courting.%20There's%20donor%20money%20to%20be%20had%20here%2C%20and%20his%20campaign%20knows%20it.%20Not%20to%20mention%20that%20Trump%20has%20long%20been%20into%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-products-that-disappeared-list-2018-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eweird%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump-university-professor-stephen-gilpin-2018-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esketchy%3C%2Fa%3E%20business%20ventures%2C%20and%20while%20not%20all%20crypto%20projects%20are%20scams%2C%20there%20does%20seem%20to%20be%20a%20lot%20of%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20Trump%2C%20you%20always%20have%20to%20view%20almost%20everything%20he%20does%20through%20the%20transactional%20lens%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Adam%20Kovacevich%2C%20the%20founder%20and%20CEO%20of%20Chamber%20of%20Progress%2C%20a%20left-leaning%20tech-industry%20coalition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20Trump's%20courting%20of%20the%20crypto%20industry%20is%20possible%20because%20Democrats%20left%20open%20an%20opportunity%20for%20him%20to%20pounce.%20President%20Joe%20Biden's%20administration%20%E2%80%94%20namely%20Gary%20Gensler%2C%20the%20chair%20of%20the%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Commission%20%E2%80%94%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcurrencies%2Fgary-gensler-sec-cryptocurrencies-bitcoin-ftx-binance-roundup-views-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etaken%20an%20antagonistic%20stance%20toward%20crypto%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Others%20in%20Biden's%20orbit%2C%20such%20as%20Lina%20Khan%2C%20the%20chair%20of%20the%20Federal%20Trade%20Commission%2C%20have%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fftc-chair-lina-khan-60-minutes-americans-privacy-big-tech-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Equite%20tough%20in%20their%20approach%20to%20the%20tech%20industry%3C%2Fa%3E%20more%20broadly.%20It%20left%20a%20bad%20taste%20in%20the%20mouths%20of%20a%20lot%20of%20powerful%20people%20in%20Silicon%20Valley%20and%20venture%20capital.%20That's%20given%20Trump%20a%20way%20to%20make%20inroads%20and%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20rake%20in%20some%20donor%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20no%20question%20that%20Trump%20and%20the%20Trump%20campaign%20were%20absolutely%20using%20crypto%20as%20a%20wedge%20against%20Biden%20because%20Biden%20had%20historically%20been%20pretty%20down%20on%20crypto%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Sheila%20Warren%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20the%20Crypto%20Council%20for%20Innovation%2C%20an%20advocacy%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20tell%20that%20the%20Trump%20camp%20thinks%20this%20is%20a%20good%20issue.%20When%20I%20reached%20out%20for%20comment%2C%20Brian%20Hughes%2C%20a%20senior%20advisor%20to%20the%20campaign%2C%20sent%20over%20a%20statement%20describing%20%26quot%3Bcrypto%20innovators%20and%20others%20in%20the%20technology%20sector%26quot%3B%20as%20%26quot%3Bunder%20attack%26quot%3B%20by%20Harris%20and%20the%20Democrats%20and%20arguing%20that%20no%20presidential%20candidate%20%26quot%3Bhas%20been%20more%20supportive%20of%20the%20crypto%20community%26quot%3B%20than%20Trump.%20The%20campaign%20also%20sent%20a%20litany%20of%20articles%20about%20various%20criticisms%20of%20crypto%20from%20left-leaning%20senators%20including%20Elizabeth%20Warren%2C%20Jon%20Tester%2C%20and%20Bernie%20Sanders.%20The%20Harris%20campaign%20declined%20to%20comment%20on%20the%20record.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump's%20interest%20in%20crypto%20isn't%20just%20political%3B%20it's%20personal%20%E2%80%94%20as%20in%20his%20personal%20finances.%20The%20billionaire-ish%20businessman%20has%20disclosed%20that%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-called-crypto-scam-now-owns-million-ethereum-disclosure-bitcoin-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eowns%20over%20%241%20million%20worth%20of%20ether%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20September%2C%20he%20unveiled%20his%20own%20crypto%20venture%2C%20World%20Liberty%20Financial.%20The%20details%20remain%20pretty%20scant%2C%20but%20some%20of%20his%20kids%20are%20into%20it%2C%20including%20his%20youngest%20son%2C%20Barron.%20It's%20fair%20to%20have%20some%20skepticism%20about%20what%20it%20will%20do%2C%20how%20it%20will%20work%2C%20and%20whether%20it's%20legitimate.%20It's%20fair%20to%20have%20the%20same%20questions%20about%20Trump's%20entire%20crypto%20pivot%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHis%20original%20approach%20on%20crypto%20was%20a%20common-sense%20recognition%20that%20it%20was%20a%20pyramid%20scheme%2C%20and%20it's%20thrown%20out%20to%20the%20wind%20because%20it's%20been%20convenient%20to%20do%20so%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Robert%20Weissman%2C%20a%20copresident%20of%20Public%20Citizen%2C%20a%20consumer%20advocacy%20group.%20%26quot%3BBut%20to%20the%20extent%20he's%20able%20to%20look%20at%20something%20cleanly%20when%20he%20did%2C%20he%20thought%20it%20was%20a%20scam.%20Now%20he's%20embraced%20it%20as%20his%20scam.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EHarris'%20advance%20into%20crypto%20on%20the%20campaign%20trail%20has%20been%20subtler%20%E2%80%94%20and%20more%20recent%20%E2%80%94%20than%20Trump's.%20She's%20not%20about%20to%20tattoo%20%26quot%3BI%20%26lt%3B3%20BTC%26quot%3B%20on%20her%20forearm%20or%20anything%3B%20she's%20just%20telling%20the%20guys%20(it's%20almost%20all%20guys)%20who%20did%20that%20that%20she's%20open%20to%20chat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20vice%20president's%20camp%20has%20reportedly%20been%20making%20overtures%20to%20the%20crypto%20industry%20for%20weeks%2C%20undertaking%20the%20endeavor%20pretty%20quickly%20after%20Biden%20dropped%20out%20of%20the%20race%20and%20she%20became%20the%20presumptive%20nominee.%20A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2Fcontent%2F1a4c5066-9cc0-4849-993b-06a28022ad66%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJuly%20report%20from%20the%20Financial%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20her%20advisors%20had%20begun%20approaching%20companies%20to%20try%20to%20%26quot%3Breset%26quot%3B%20the%20relationship%20with%20the%20industry%20and%20put%20out%20feelers%20about%20meeting%20with%20firms%20such%20as%20Coinbase%20and%20Circle.%20A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.politico.com%2Fnews%2F2024%2F07%2F26%2Fkamala-harris-donald-trump-crypto-00171365%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPolitico%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20about%20the%20same%20time%20described%20crypto%20advocates%20as%20hopeful%20about%20Harris%2C%20given%20that%20she's%20from%20California%2C%20a%20tech-heavy%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20early%20August%2C%20volunteers%20organized%20a%20Crypto4Harris%20town%20hall%20that%20was%20attended%20by%20Senate%20Majority%20Leader%20Chuck%20Schumer%2C%20Gov.%20Jared%20Polis%20of%20Colorado%2C%20the%20Wall%20Street%20financier%20Anthony%20Scaramucci%2C%20and%20the%20billionaire%20investor%20Mark%20Cuban.%20Ron%20Conway%2C%20a%20Democratic%20megadonor%20and%20venture%20capitalist%20who%20stopped%20supporting%20crypto%20super%20PACs%20after%20they%20began%20spending%20against%20Sherrod%20Brown%2C%20has%20been%20optimistic%20about%20Harris.%20In%20July%2C%20he%20called%20for%20the%20tech%20community%20to%20unite%20behind%20Harris%20and%20defeat%20Trump.%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20known%20Kamala%20for%20decades%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3Band%20she's%20been%20a%20fighter%2C%20a%20leader%2C%20and%20an%20advocate%20for%20the%20tech%20ecosystem%20since%20the%20day%20we%20met.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20campaign's%20outreach%20inspired%20some%20cautious%20enthusiasm%20in%20the%20crypto%20community%2C%20but%20there's%20a%20difference%20between%20a%20candidate's%20surrogates%20saying%20something%20and%20the%20candidate%20saying%20it%20themselves%2C%20which%20is%20what%20some%20in%20the%20industry%20were%20waiting%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20late%20September%2C%20Harris%20addressed%20crypto%20directly%20at%20a%20weekend%20Wall%20Street%20fundraiser%20in%20New%20York%2C%20where%20she%20said%20her%20administration%20would%20%26quot%3Bencourage%20innovative%20technologies%20like%20AI%20and%20digital%20assets%20while%20protecting%20our%20consumers%20and%20investors.%26quot%3B%20A%20few%20days%20later%2C%20she%20reiterated%20her%20support%20in%20a%20speech%20on%20the%20economy%2C%20saying%20the%20US%20would%20remain%20dominant%20in%20%26quot%3BAI%2C%20quantum%20computing%2C%20blockchain%2C%20and%20other%20emerging%20technologies.%26quot%3B%20She's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.semafor.com%2Farticle%2F09%2F26%2F2024%2Fharris-escalates-her-courtship-of-crypto%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereportedly%20dispatched%20aides%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20do%20more%20outreach.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20way%20to%20read%20Harris'%20efforts%20is%20as%20a%20sort%20of%20olive%20branch%20to%20the%20tech%20community%2C%20a%20signal%20to%20Silicon%20Valley%2C%20venture%20capital%2C%20and%20startups%20that%20she's%20not%20aligned%20with%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump-vcs-in-silicon-valley-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBiden%20administration's%20hard-nosed%20approach%20to%20tech%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20makes%20it%20easier%20for%20donors%20who%20were%20hesitant%20to%20support%20her%20to%20finally%20throw%20in%2C%20and%20her%20openness%20to%20conversation%20puts%20some%20tech%20minds%20at%20ease.%20It's%20about%20crypto%2C%20but%20it's%20also%20more%20than%20that.%20By%20coupling%20mentions%20of%20digital%20assets%20and%20blockchain%20with%20AI%2C%20Harris%20weaves%20it%20into%20her%20broader%20economic%20message%20about%20innovation%20and%20entrepreneurship.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Biden%20administration%20has%20been%20so%20hostile%20to%20crypto%20that%20the%20main%20challenge%20for%20the%20Harris%20campaign%20has%20been%20to%20say%20in%20a%20clear%20and%20credible%20way%20that%20they%20recognize%20that%20and%20they%20want%20to%20depart%20from%20that%20strategy%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Rachael%20Horwitz%2C%20the%20chief%20marketing%20officer%20at%20Haun%20Ventures%2C%20a%20venture-capital%20firm.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20big%20hill%20to%20climb%20because%20so%20much%20trust%20has%20been%20lost.%26quot%3B%20Horwitz%20added%20that%20before%20Harris'%20late-September%20remarks%2C%20%26quot%3Bthere%20were%20only%20campaign%20surrogates%20asking%20the%20industry%20to%20take%20their%20word%20for%20it%20that%20behind%20the%20scenes%20she%20is%20more%20pro-tech%20and%20pro-innovation%20than%20Biden.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20be%20sure%2C%20Harris%20hasn't%20spoken%20at%20length%20about%20crypto%2C%20and%20what%20she%20has%20said%20is%20quite%20vague%20and%20generic.%20It's%20a%20stance%20a%20lot%20of%20policymakers%20hold%20%E2%80%94%20yes%2C%20we%20want%20to%20foster%20innovation%2C%20and%20yes%2C%20we%20want%20to%20protect%20consumers%20in%20the%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Molly%20White%2C%20a%20crypto%20researcher%20and%20critic%2C%20described%20Harris'%20recent%20statements%20about%20crypto%20as%20%26quot%3Bmiddle%20of%20the%20road%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20she%20thought%20the%20crypto%20industry%20was%20%26quot%3Bdefinitely%20taking%20an%20optimistic%20view.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUltimately%20the%20question%20is%20not%20only%20what%20will%20the%20candidates%20say%20but%20what%20will%20they%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHorwitz%20said%20she%20saw%20this%20as%20%26quot%3Ba%20longer-term%20issue%20that%20goes%20beyond%20statements%20during%20a%20campaign%20where%20action%20is%20the%20only%20real%20path%20to%20signaling%20to%20founders%20and%20the%20venture%20community%20that%20whomever%20is%20president%20believes%20that%20blockchain%20technology%20is%20here%20to%20stay%20and%20America%20should%20lead.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3ECrypto%20is%20not%20going%20to%20decide%20the%202024%20election%3B%20issues%20like%20abortion%20and%20immigration%20and%20the%20economy%20and%20overall%20vibes%20are%20going%20to%20do%20that.%20But%20the%20industry%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-bitcoin-mines-american-electricity-china-crypto-ban-energy-crisis-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eamassed%20some%20significant%20financial%20power%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethat%20it's%20clearly%20willing%20to%20wield%20politically%2C%20and%20that%20can%20be%20tough%20for%20politicians%20to%20ignore.%20It's%20got%20some%20sway%20in%20the%20political%20discourse%2C%20too%2C%20as%20prominent%20crypto%20figures%20weigh%20in%20on%20the%20race%20and%20deploy%20their%20donations%20accordingly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20grand%20narrative%20of%20crypto%20of%20the%20industry%20spending%20a%20ton%20of%20money%20and%20shifting%20the%20center%20of%20gravity%20on%20crypto%20policy%2C%20including%20by%20making%20it%20something%20that%20politicians%20feel%20they%20have%20to%20talk%20about%2C%20when%20it's%20really%20overall%20pretty%20unimportant%20and%20not%20something%20on%20anybody's%20radar%2C%26quot%3B%20Weissman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20statistic%20crypto%20boosters%20typically%20deploy%20is%20that%20about%20one%20in%20five%20Americans%20have%20owned%20crypto%2C%20the%20argument%20being%20that%20that%20ownership%20will%20affect%20their%20votes.%20It's%20a%20dubious%20claim%20%E2%80%94%20just%20because%20you%20have%20%2450%20in%20bitcoin%20doesn't%20mean%20it's%20determining%20what%20you%20do%20in%20November.%20There%20isn't%20a%20huge%20block%20of%20crypto%20voters%20up%20for%20grabs.%20But%20given%20how%20close%20the%20race%20is%2C%20a%20light%20appeal%20probably%20doesn't%20hurt%20any%20candidate.%20Trump%20is%20clearly%20targeting%20young%20men%2C%20and%20crypto%20is%20a%20thing%20they%20like.%20The%20problem%20is%20that%20young%20men%20generally%20aren't%20rushing%20to%20the%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAre%20they%20winnable%3F%20Sure.%20Are%20they%20going%20to%20vote%3F%20Who%20the%20heck%20knows%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Dan%20Cassino%2C%20a%20professor%20of%20government%20and%20politics%20at%20Fairleigh%20Dickinson%20University%20who%20researches%20polling%20and%20masculinity.%20%26quot%3BGetting%20people%20under%2025%2C%20under%2030%20to%20vote%20is%20hard%20for%20any%20campaign.%20But%20getting%20especially%20men%20under%2030%20to%20vote%2C%20no%20one%20even%20bothers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20crypto%20industry%20doesn't%20mind%20the%20attention%20it's%20getting%20from%20policymakers.%20It%20helps%20crypto%20executives%20get%20meetings%20on%20Capitol%20Hill%20to%20try%20to%20craft%20favorable%20legislation.%20It%20gets%20them%20the%20ears%20of%20lawmakers%20who%20might%20ultimately%20decide%20how%20their%20companies%20are%20regulated%20and%20by%20whom.%20At%20the%20presidential%20level%2C%20there%20are%20some%20appointees%20that%20the%20crypto%20and%20tech%20industries%20would%20very%20much%20like%20to%20be%20out%20%E2%80%94%20Gensler%20at%20the%20SEC%2C%20Khan%20at%20the%20FTC.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20very%20clear%20from%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20reporting%20that%20Harris%20has%20gotten%20an%20earful%20from%20people%20in%20the%20business%20community%20about%20Gensler%20and%20crypto%20and%20about%20Lina%20Khan%20and%20the%20FTC%2C%26quot%3B%20Kovacevich%2C%20at%20the%20Chamber%20of%20Progress%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECrypto%20companies%2C%20like%20most%20businesses%2C%20don't%20really%20want%20to%20make%20partisan%20enemies.%20To%20get%20things%20done%20in%20Washington%2C%20it's%20a%20good%20idea%20to%20have%20friends%20on%20both%20sides%20of%20the%20aisle%2C%20even%20if%20not%20everyone%20is%20a%20bestie.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCrypto%20is%20purple%2C%26quot%3B%20Warren%2C%20from%20the%20Crypto%20Council%20for%20Innovation%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20Harris%20or%20Trump%20will%20actually%20do%20on%20crypto%20is%20unclear%2C%20but%20that's%20not%20really%20the%20point%20right%20now.%20The%20point%20is%20to%20make%20nice%20with%20tech%20and%20try%20to%20win%20in%20November.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%