%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFIRE%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20financial%20independence%2C%20retire%20early%20%E2%80%94%20movement%2C%20he%20cut%20back%20on%20excess%20purchases%2C%20tracked%20all%20his%20expenses%2C%20invested%20in%20rental%20properties%2C%20and%20maxed%20out%20his%20401(k)%20and%20IRA.%20Despite%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillionaire-investing-saving-spending-financial-independence-retire-early-fire-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enot%20having%20a%20flashy%20job%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20he%20and%20his%20wife%20carefully%20crafted%20their%20financial%20portfolio%20to%20grow%20their%20wealth%20without%20sacrificing%20travel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20conversation%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennials-retiring-early-fire-movement-financial-independence-millionaire-savings-work-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFIRE%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20it's%20almost%20like%20looking%20at%20the%20end%2C%20but%20part%20of%20it%20is%20looking%20at%20the%20beginning%20too%2C%26quot%3B%20Delva-Gonzalez%20said.%20%26quot%3BNot%20everyone%20starts%20off%20rich%2C%20and%20I%20didn't%20start%20off%20rich%20at%20all.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220de01abd-85f7-45f6-b0bd-581667035fe4%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20challenging%20financial%20beginning%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDelva-Gonzalez%20was%20born%20in%20the%20US%20but%20raised%20in%20Haiti%20by%20his%20grandmother.%20Growing%20up%2C%20he%20said%20most%20of%20Port-au-Prince%20could%20be%20classified%20as%20%26quot%3Bworking%20poor%2C%26quot%3B%20including%20his%20grandmother%20who%20would%20wake%20up%20at%204%20a.m.%20working%20side%20hustles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20noted%20how%20everyone%20in%20his%20neighborhood%20shared%20food%2C%20as%20his%20grandmother%20would%20prepare%20a%20large%20pot%20of%20food%20and%20serve%20those%20in%20need.%20He%20recalled%20having%20no%20AC%20or%20clean%20running%20water%20growing%20up%20and%20few%20books%20in%20his%20school%20library.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThose%20little%20things%20taught%20me%20how%20to%20value%20not%20just%20making%20money%20but%20how%20to%20use%20it%20to%20provide%20a%20roof%20over%20my%20head%20and%20food%20in%20the%20pantry%2C%26quot%3B%20Delva-Gonzalez%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20he%20was%20a%20teenager%2C%20he%20moved%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbillionaire-bunker-miami-bezos-tom-brady-ivanka-trump-security-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMiami%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20his%20mother%20into%20a%20studio%20apartment.%20His%20mother%20never%20made%20more%20than%20%2430%2C000%20a%20year%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20were%20poor.%20I%20don't%20know%20why%20people%20don't%20like%20to%20say%20it%2C%20but%20it's%20just%20what%20it%20was%2C%26quot%3B%20Delva-Gonzalez%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20got%20reduced%20breakfasts%20and%20lunches%20at%20school.%20The%20first%20time%20I%20had%20tennis%20shoes%20when%20when%20I%20bought%20them%20for%20myself%20when%20I%20was%2016%20because%20I%20had%20to%20work.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20decided%20to%20attend%20college%2C%20taking%20out%20%24110%2C000%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprofessor-student-loan-debt-suddenly-forgiven-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estudent%20loans%3C%2Fa%3E%20between%20his%20undergraduate%20and%20graduate%20programs%20in%20business%20and%20accounting%20at%20Florida%20State%20University.%20He%20also%20spent%20seven%20years%20in%20the%20Marine%20Corps.%20Being%20in%20debt%20stressed%20him%20out%20immensely%2C%20though%20he%20struggled%20to%20secure%20a%20high-paying%20job%2C%20especially%20since%20it%20took%20him%20a%20few%20years%20to%20become%20acclimated%20to%20American%20culture.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20suspected%20his%20racial%20and%20socioeconomic%20background%20hindered%20him%20in%20the%20job%20search%2C%20and%20he%20was%20once%20told%20in%20an