20make%20a%20better%20impression.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjd-vance-unpopularity-struggles-polls-vp-debate-walz-trump-harris-2024-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727688662000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66f7ed467518aa57bc9f030c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjd-vance-unpopularity-struggles-polls-vp-debate-walz-trump-harris-2024-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Poll%20averages%20show%20that%20JD%20Vance%20is%20the%20least%20liked%20of%20the%20four%20major%20figures%20in%20the%202024%20race.%20Tuesday's%20VP%20debate%20is%20his%20best%20chance%20to%20change%20that.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22bgriffiths%40insider.com%20(Brent%20D.%20Griffiths)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A19%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjd-vance-unpopularity-struggles-polls-vp-debate-walz-trump-harris-2024-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Stock%20market%20investing%3A%20Changes%20in%20transaction%20charges%2C%20STT%2C%20buyback%20taxation%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727688600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-113810948%2Cimgsize-93944.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Findia-business%2Fstock-market-investors-take-note-3-changes-in-transaction-charges-stt-buyback-taxation-from-october-1-2024-you-should-know%2Farticleshow%2F113809951.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22From%20October%201%2C%202024%2C%20Indian%20stock%20market%20investors%20will%20encounter%20revised%20transaction%20fees%20from%20BSE%20and%20NSE%2C%20increased%20securities%20transaction%20tax%20on%20futures%20and%20options%20trading%2C%20and%20new%20taxation%20rules%20for%20share%20buybacks.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20BUSINESS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canon