never%20we%20go%20out%20on%20a%20rescue%2C%20we%20are%20supported%20by%20jet%20skis%2C%20backup%20lifeguards%2C%20etc.%20Also%2C%20we%20receive%20continuous%20training%20and%20have%20reorientation%20sessions%20every%20year%20to%20keep%20up%20with%20the%20latest%20methods%20and%20technology%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Shashikant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBraving%20the%20waves%3A%20Goa%E2%80%99s%20Drishti%20Marine%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20news%20of%20Drishti%20becoming%20the%20designated%20agency%20to%20provide%20lifeguard%20services%20also%20prompted%20Ashwin%20Ghag%2C%20a%20former%20national-level%20swimmer%2C%20to%20leave%20Pune%20for%20Goa%20in%202008.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFrom%201999%20to%202008%2C%20I%20worked%20as%20a%20swimming%20coach%20for%20children%20in%20Pune%2C%20after%20which%20I%20worked%20as%20a%20senior%20lifeguard.%20Before%20my%20swimming%20coach%20and%20lifeguard%20career%2C%20I%20was%20a%20national-level%20swimmer.%20I%20was%20inspired%20by%20my%20father%20to%20become%20a%20lifeguard.%20Watching%20him%20work%20as%20a%20lifeguard%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F159192%2Fpune-drowning-lives-raju%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esave%20lives%3C%2Fa%3E%20inspired%20me%20to%20become%20one%2C%E2%80%9D%20recalls%20Ashwin%2C%20a%2042-year-old%20senior%20lifeguard%20at%20Drishti%20Marine%20currently%20posted%20on%20the%20popular%20and%20crowded%20Calangute%20beach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FShashikant-And-Ashwin-1727448721.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lifeguards%20-%20Shashikant%20Jadhav%20and%20Ashwin%20Ghag.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FShashikant-And-Ashwin-1727448721.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FShashikant-And-Ashwin-1727448721-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FShashikant-And-Ashwin-1727448721-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FShashikant-And-Ashwin-1727448721-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FShashikant-And-Ashwin-1727448721-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-367902%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EShashikant%20Jadhav%20and%20Ashwin%20Ghag%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20I%20was%20working%20in%20Pune%2C%20I%20heard%20about%20a%20new%20company%20in%20Goa%20offering%20lifeguarding%20services%20and%20that%20they%20needed%20lifeguards.%20Along%20with%20another%20senior%20lifeguard%20from%20Pune%2C%20I%20moved%20to%20Goa.%20Despite%20my%20skills%2C%20I%20had%20little%20experience%20of%20working%20on%20beaches.%20Working%20as%20a%20lifeguard%20in%20swimming%20pools%2C%20I%20knew%20how%20to%20use%20life-saving%20equipment.%20But%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20how%20to%20use%20them%20in%20the%20sea%20due%20to%20my%20lack%20of%20experience%20working%20in%20these%20surroundings%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20thing%20Ashwin%20learnt%20after%20joining%20Drishti%20was%20how%20much%20more%20stamina%20a%20lifeguard%20requires%20to%20swim%20into%20a%20massive%20water%20body%20like%20the%20Arabian%20Sea%20and%20rescue%20someone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20saving%20someone%20from%20drowning%20in%20a%20swimming%20pool%2C%20you%20are%20working%20in%20a%20confined%20space%20with%20four%20corners%20no%20matter%20its%20size.%20You%20know%20exactly%20where%20to%20jump%20in%2C%20save%20the%20person%20and%20drop%20them%20off%20at%20any%20given%20edge%20of%20the%20pool.%20In%20the%20sea%2C%20you%20can%20only%20save%20someone%20by%20taking%20them%20back%20one%20way.%20It%E2%80%99s%20not%20a%20confined%20space.%20Another%20thing%20I%20learnt%20about%20were%20rip%20currents%20%E2%80%94%20strong%20and%20narrow%20currents%20that%20can%20pull%20you%20into%20the%20water%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ashwin.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20Drishti%20Marine%20is%20the%20designated%20first%20responder%20for%20any%20beach-related%20emergency%2C%20including%20cases%20of%20marine%20strandings.%20Since%20its%20inception%2C%20Rajiv%20claims%20that%20its%20450-plus%20strong%20force%20of%20%E2%80%98lifesavers%E2%80%99%20(lifeguards)%20has%20saved%20about%207%2C700%20people%20from%20drowning%20off%20Goa%E2%80%99s%20coastline.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EPatrolling%20Goa%E2%80%99s%20shores%20and%20saving%20lives%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeaches%20in%20Goa%20are%20divided%20into%20zones%3A%20swim%20areas%20marked%20by%20red%20and%20yellow%20flags%2C%20no-swim%20zones%20by%20red%20flags%2C%20and%20watersport%20areas%20by%20black-and-white%20flags.%20High-footfall%20beaches%20have%20dedicated%20lifesaver%20towers%20offering%20a%20clear%20vantage%20point.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Rajiv%20elaborates%2C%20%E2%80%9CSwim%20zones%20are%20continuously%20monitored%20by%20lifesavers%20equipped%20with%20binoculars%2C%20jet%20skis%2C%20spine%20boards%2C%20surfboards%2C%20and%20rescue%20tubes.%20When%20a%20person%20in%20distress%20is%20spotted%20off%20the%20beach%2C%20the%20on-duty%20lifesaver%20notifies%20other%20lifesavers%20via%20radio.%20The%20rescue%20team%20rushes%20to%20assist%20the%20person%20in%20distress%2C%20alerts%20backup%20to%20call%20an%20ambulance%2C%20and%20accompanies%20the%20rescued%20individual%20to%20the%20hospital%20for%20evaluation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%2