nts%20or%20distressed%20individuals%20to%20nearby%20health%20facilities%20or%20ambulances.%20Lifesavers%20are%20also%20trained%20in%20first%20aid%20to%20provide%20immediate%20assistance%20during%20medical%20emergencies%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWorking%20in%20Calangute%20beach%2C%20I%20do%20approximately%2030%20rescues%20a%20month%20because%20there%20is%20always%20a%20large%20crowd%20present%20there.%20Rescues%20usually%20happen%20between%20an%20approximate%20range%20of%2030%20to%2050%20metres%20into%20the%20sea%20%5Bfrom%20the%20shoreline%5D.%20Away%20from%20the%20shoreline%20at%20Calangute%20Beach%2C%20we%20encounter%20a%20lot%20of%20rip%20currents.%20When%20a%20tourist%20encounters%20a%20rip%20current%20by%20swimming%20too%20far%20from%20the%20shore%2C%20they%20panic%20because%20the%20water%20is%20pulling%20them%20into%20the%20sea%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Ashwin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20are%20the%20heroes%20behind%20the%20rescues%20chosen%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMen%20and%20women%20between%20the%20ages%20of%2018%20and%2030%20years%20who%20know%20swimming%20and%20are%20committed%20to%20saving%20victims%20are%20eligible%20to%20become%20Drishti%20lifesavers%2C%20notes%20Rajiv.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9COur%20hiring%20checklist%20includes%20thorough%20physical%20tests%2C%20interviews%2C%20reference%20checks%2C%20and%20police%20verification.%20The%20physically%20demanding%20nature%20of%20a%20lifesaver%20requires%20that%20men%20and%20women%20who%20apply%20should%20possess%20a%20high%20degree%20of%20physical%20fitness%20and%20our%20training%20team%20does%20the%20rest.%20Every%20lifesaver%20must%20be%20capable%20of%20swimming%20400%20metres%20in%20under%2011%20minutes.%20They%20need%20to%20quickly%20assess%20the%20capabilities%20and%20risks%20of%20individuals%20involved%20in%20aquatic%20activities%2C%20follow%20on-site%20protocols%2C%20and%20provide%20emergency%20medical%20services%20when%20required%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Rajiv.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajiv%20goes%20on%20to%20claim%2C%20%E2%80%9CDrishti%E2%80%99s%20450-strong%20lifesaver%20team%20undergoes%20a%20rigorous%20annual%20refresher%20course%20to%20maintain%20and%20improve%20their%20emergency%20response%20skills%2C%20physical%20fitness%2C%20and%20communication%20abilities.%20The%20training%20includes%20CPR%2C%20first%20aid%2C%20beach%20operations%2C%20jet%20ski%20use%2C%20rescue%20equipment%20handling%2C%20and%20various%20rescue%20techniques.%20In%20addition%20to%20lifesaving%20skills%2C%20they%20also%20receive%20training%20in%20leadership%20and%20soft%20skills%20to%20effectively%20manage%20public%20interactions.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll%20data-origheight%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2Fe9DZo2iJaDg%3Fenablejsapi%3D1%26rel%3D0%26modestbranding%3D0%26autoplay%3D0%26cc_load_policy%3D0%26iv_load_policy%3D3%26loop%3D0%26fs%3D1%26playsinline%3D1%26controls%3D1%26color%3Dred%26cc_lang_pref%3D%26autohide%3D2%26theme%3Ddark%26%5C%22%20data-no-lazy%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20player%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20data-origwidth%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELifesavers%20must%20complete%20annual%20training%20to%20retain%20their%20certification%20and%20remain%20eligible%20for%20duty.%20This%20programme%2C%20conducted%20across%20both%20Goan%20districts%2C%20is%20organised%20by%20the%20Special%20Rescue%20Training%20Academy%20(SRTA)%2C%20affiliated%20with%20the%20National%20Skill%20Development%20Council%2C%