Cn%3Cp%3EHussain%20was%20later%20found%20with%20his%20head%20smashed%20in%20the%20field.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20rhino%20came%20out%20of%20the%20wildlife%20sanctuary.%20We%20are%20investigating%20the%20incident%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20forest%20official%20told%20the%20news%20agency%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELocated%20in%20the%20suburbs%20of%20Assam's%20capital%20Guwahati%2C%20the%20Pobitora%20Wildlife%20Sanctuary%20is%20known%20for%20holding%20the%20highest%20density%20of%20one-horned%20rhinos%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EData%20released%20this%20month%20on%20World%20Rhino%20Day%20said%20that%20India's%20one-horned%20Asian%20rhino%20population%20has%20almost%20tripled%20in%20the%20past%20four%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20number%20of%20animals%20has%20surged%20from%201%2C500%20four%20decades%20ago%20to%20more%20than%204%2C000%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20adult%20Indian%20rhino%2C%20the%20largest%20of%20the%20three%20Asian%20species%2C%20can%20live%20for%20about%2050%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F6-rhinos-among-137-animals-dead-in-kaziranga-national-park-amid-assam-floods-6064265%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKaziranga%20National%20Park%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Assam%20is%20home%20to%20an%20estimated%2080%20percent%20of%20the%20world's%20one-horned%20rhinos.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727680860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2F4libfjeo_assam-rhino-attack_625x300_30_September_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fon-camera-biker-chased-and-attacked-by-rhino-in-assam-near-pobitora-wildlife-sanctuary-dies-6681749%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20biker%20died%20after%20being%20chased%20and%20attacked%20by%20a%20rhino%20near%20the%20Pobitora%20Wildlife%20Sanctuary%20in%20Assam's%20Morigaon%20district%20on%20Sunday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fon-camera-biker-chased-and-attacked-by-rhino-in-assam-near-pobitora-wildlife-sanctuary-dies-6681749%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20J%26amp%3BK%20Election%3A%2010%20Years%20On%2C%20Which%20Way%20Will%20The%20Wind%20Blow%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fjirkee9o_kahsmir_625x300_24_September_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20third%20and%20final%20round%20of%20voting%20for%20the%20Jammu%20%26amp%3B%20Kashmir%20elections%20will%20be%20held%20tomorrow%20(October%201).%20This%20is%20the%20first%20assembly%20poll%20in%20the%20erstwhile%20state%20after%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20last%2010%20years%20have%20seen%20momentous%20changes%20in%20the%20political%20complexion%20of%20the%20region.%20Soon%20after%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20Article%20370%2C%20which%20gave%20a%20special%20status%20to%20the%20state%2C%20was%20rescinded.%20Further%2C%20it%20was%20divided%20into%20two%20Union%20Territories%20%E2%80%93%20Ladakh%20and%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20has%20promised%20to%20restore%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir's%20statehood%20in%20future.%20And%20while%20a%20few%20regional%20players%20have%20sought%20a%20restoration%20of%20the%20special%20status%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20been%20non-committal%20on%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Lok%20Sabha%20Contest%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20assembly%20polls%20in%20Jammu%20%26amp%3B%20Kashmir%20this%20year%20were%20preceded%20by%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%20The%20BJP%20contested%20two%20seats%20in%20the%20Jammu%20region%20and%20won%20both.%20In%20the%20remaining%20three%20seats%20in%20Kashmir%2C%20the%20National%20Conference%20(NC)%20won%20two%20and%20an%20Independent%20candidate%20was%20elected%20from%20one.%20The%20People's%20Democratic%20Party%20(PDP)%20was%20unable%20to%20open%20its%20account.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20key%20leaders%20of%20the%20NC%20and%20the%20PDP%2C%20Omar%20Abdullah%20and%20Mehbooba%20Mufti%2C%20lost%20the%20elections.%20Abdullah%20was%20defeated%20by%20an%20independent%20candidate%2C%20Engineer%20Rashid%20(who%20contested%20the%20elections%20from%20jail)%2C%20while%20Mufti%20lost%20to%20the%20NC's%20Mian%20Altaf%20Ahmed%20Larvi.%20Both%20fell%20behind%20by%20over%202%20lakh%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20the%2090%20assembly%20segments%20are%20taken%20into%20account%20for%20the%20results%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20contest%2C%20then%20the%20National%20Conference%20led%20in%2036%20assembly%20seats%20and%20its%20alliance%20partner%2C%20the%20Congress%2C%20was%20ahead%20in%20seven%2C%20bringing%20their%20combined%20strength%20close%20to%20the%20half-way%20mark.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20BJP%20led%20in%2029%20segments%2C%20the%20PDP%20in%20five%2C%20and%20Independents%20and%20others%20in%20the%20remaining%2013%20seats.%20The%20NC%20and%20the%20BJP%20improved%20their%20performance%20compared%20to%20the%202014%20assembly%20polls%2C%20while%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20PDP%20faced%20a%20sharp%20decline.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E3%20Reasons%20This%20Election%20Is%20So%20Critical%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20current%20assembly%20election%20has%20evoked%20tremendous%20interest%20both%20within%20the%20country%20and%20internationally%20for%20multiple%20reasons.%20The%20verdict%20will%20reflect%20the%20popular%20mood%20after%20the%20Article%20370%20move%20and%20the%20subsequent%20developments%20in%20the%20region.%20That%20this%20is%20the%20first%20election%20in%2010%20years%20also%20means%20that%20there%20is%20a%20whole%20new%20generation%20of%20voters%20-%20those%20in%20the%20age%20group%20of%2018-28%20%E2%80%94%20that%20is%20voting%20for%20the%20first%20time.%20The%20group%20represents%20an%20important%20segment%20of%20the%20electorate.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20three%20dimensions%20that%20assume%20importance%20in%20the%20current%20Jammu%20%26amp%3B%20Kashmir%20election.%20The%20first%20is%20the%20voter%20turnout%2C%20which%20many%20see%20as%20a%20barometer%20to%20measure%20the%20popular%20response%20to%20the%20democratic%20process%20in%20the%20state.%20The%20first%20phase%20of%20polling%20saw%20over%2061%25%20voting%2C%20while%20the%20second%20phase%20saw%2057%25%20of%20electors%20coming%20out%20to%20vote.%20In%202014%2C%20the%20assembly%20polls%20had%20attracted%20a%2065%25%20turnout%20despite%20a%20boycott%20call.%20Thus%2C%20while%20the%20initial%20numbers%20this%20year%20may%20seem%20lower%2C%20they%20still%20represent%20a%20strong%20turnout.%20It%20is%20also%20important%20to%20note%20that%20the%20first%20two%20phases%20of%20voting%20were%20free%20of%20violence%20and%20saw%20peaceful%20polling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECounting%20is%20scheduled%20for%20October%208.%20Media%20reports%20indicate%20that%20for%20the%20younger%20generation%2C%20especially%2C%20economic%20issues%20like%20development%2C%20employment%2C%20price%20rise%2C%20and%20peace%20and%20security%20are%20key%20factors%20that%20influenced%20their%20decision.%20The%20two%20regional%20parties%2C%20the%20NC%20and%20the%20PDP%2C%20have%20focused%20on%20their%20demand%20for%20the%20restoration%20of%20Article%20370%20and%20statehood.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Fate%20Of%20Old%20Players%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Jammu%20region%20and%20the%20Kashmir%20valley%20have%20distinctly%20different%20political%20orientations.%20In%20recent%20times%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20had%20an%20upper%20hand%20in%20Jammu%2C%20while%20the%20Congress%2C%20the%20NC%20and%20the%20PDP%20have%20been%20key%20players%20in%20the%20Kashmir%20valley.%20The%20final%20result%20would%20be%20a%20clear%20indication%20of%20how%20much%20support%20these%20players%20have%20across%20the%20region%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20leads%20one%20to%20the%20third%20and%20last%20factor%20due%20to%20which%20the%20current%20assembly%20polls%20are%20significant.%20This%20election%20has%20seen%20the%20entry%20of%20several%20new%20local%20parties%20and%20independent%20candidates%2C%20whose%20performance%20will%20be%20watched%20closely.%20Do%20national%20parties%20and%20traditional%20regional%20players%20continue%20to%20hold%20sway%2C%20or%20have%20new%20players%20tipped%20the%20scales%3F%20The%20answer%20to%20this%20would%20also%20be%20a%20reflection%20of%20the%20cut%20and%20thrust%20of%20the%20overall%20politics%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Dr.%20Sandeep%20Shastri%20is%20the%20National%20Coordinator%20of%20the%20Lokniti%20Network)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727680800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fjirkee9o_kahsmir_625x300_24_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fj-k-election-10-years-on-which-way-will-the-wind-blow-6682102%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Jammu%20region%20and%20the%20Kashmir%20valley%20have%20distinctly%20different%20political%20orientations.%20The%20final%20result%20would%20be%20a%20clear%20indication%20of%20how%20much%20support%20these%20political%20players%20have%20across%20the%20region%20today.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fj-k-election-10-years-on-which-way-will-the-wind-blow-6682102%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Explained%3A%20What%20Is%20Marburg%20Virus%20That%20Has%20Killed%206%20In%20This%20African%20Country%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAt%20least%20six%20people%20have%20died%20in%20Rwanda's%20first-ever%20outbreak%20of%20the%20deadly%20Marburg%20virus.%20Sabin%20Nsanzimana%2C%20the%20country's%20health%20minister%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fafrica.cgtn.com%2Fsix-dead-as-rwanda-battles-marburg-virus-outbreak%2F%C2%A0%5C%22%3Econfirmed%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20most%20of%20the%20victims%20were%20healthcare%20workers%20in%20a%20hospital%20intensive%20care%20unit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwenty-six%20cases%20have%20been%20confirmed%20since%20Friday.%20Authorities%20are%20tracking%20around%20300%20people%20who%20may%20have%20been%20exposed%20to%20the%20virus%2C%20mostly%20in%20the%20capital%20city%2C%20Kigali.%20To%20curb%20its%20spread%2C%20the%20government%20is%20implementing%20measures%20such%20as%20contact%20tracing%2C%20quarantining%20affected%20individuals%20and%20launching%20public%20health%20awareness%20campaigns.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20the%20Marburg%20Virus%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Marburg%20virus%20is%20a%20highly%20infectious%20disease%20similar%20to%20Ebola.%20According%20to%20the%20World%20Health%20Organisation%2C%20the%20disease%20has%20a%20high%20fatality%20rate%2C%20ranging%20from%2024%20per%20cent%20to%2088%20per%20cent%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20outbreak%20and%20the%20healthcare%20response.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20virus%20was%20first%20identified%20in%201967.%20This%20outbreak%2C%20linked%20to%20African%20green%20monkeys%20imported%20from%20Uganda%2C%20occurred%20simultaneously%20in%20Marburg%20and%20Frankfurt%20in%20Germany%20and%20Belgrade%20in%20Serbia%2C%20leading%20to%2031%20infections%20and%20seven%20deaths%20at%20the%20time.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3EHow%20the%20virus%20spreads%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20primary%20carrier%20of%20the%20Marburg%20virus%20is%20the%20Egyptian%20rousette%20fruit%20bat%2C%20which%20can%20transmit%20the%20virus%20to%20humans.%20African%20green%20monkeys%20and%20pigs%20can%20also%20carry%20the%20virus.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20virus%20spreads%20between%20humans%20through%20contact%20with%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBodily%20fluids%20(blood%2C%20saliva%2C%20vomit%2C%20etc)%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EContaminated%20bedding%20or%20surfaces%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EInfected%20semen%2C%20which%20can%20remain%20infectious%20months%20after%20recovery%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESymptoms%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnSymptoms%20can%20start%20suddenly%20and%20include%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EHigh%20fever%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESevere%20headaches%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMuscle%20pains%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20about%20three%20days%2C%20patients%20report%20severe%20symptoms%20such%20as%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWatery%20diarrhoea%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EStomach%20pain%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EVomiting%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBleeding%20from%20various%20parts%20of%20the%20body%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20WHO%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20appearance%20of%20patients%20at%20this%20phase%20has%20been%20described%20as%20showing%20'ghost-like'%20drawn%20features%2C%20deep-set%20eyes%2C%20expressionless%20faces%20and%20extreme%20lethargy.%E2%80%9D%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnExtreme%20blood%20loss%20and%20shock%20can%20result%20in%20death%20within%20eight%20to%20nine%20days%20after%20symptoms%20appear.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3ECurrent%20control%20measures%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnHealth%20authorities%20recommend%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAvoiding%20physical%20contact%20with%20the%20infected%20people%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWashing%20hands%20regularly%20with%20soap%20and%20water%20or%20using%20sanitiser%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAvoiding%20consumption%20of%20bushmeat%20or%20contact%20with%20pigs%20in%20outbreak%20areas%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20WHO%20is%20providing%20support%20to%20Rwanda%20in%20managing%20the%20outbreak.%20There%20are%20currently%20no%20specific%20treatments%20or%20vaccines%2C%20although%20supportive%20care%2C%20including%20fluid%20replacement%20and%20blood%20transfusions%2C%20may%20help%20manage%20symptoms.%20Researchers%20are%20developing%20various%20blood%20products%2C%20drug%20therapies%2C%20and%20immune%20treatments.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727680560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-06%2Fh2ihbnsg_virus-generic_625x300_04_June_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmarburg-virus-outbreak-in-rwanda-what-is-it-symptoms-cure-6681999%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22At%20least%20six%20people%20have%20died%20in%20Rwanda's%20first-ever%20outbreak%20of%20the%20deadly%20Marburg%20virus.%20Sabin%20Nsanzimana%2C%20the%20country's%20health%20minister%2C%20confirmed%20that%20most%20of%20the%20victims%20were%20healthcare%20workers%20in%20a%20hospital%20intensive%20care%20unit.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmarburg-virus-outbreak-in-rwanda-what-is-it-symptoms-cure-6681999%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kangana's%20Emergency%20to%20make%20changes%20to%20film%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727680476000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-113806790%2Cimgsize-23208.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fkangana-ranauts-emergency-makers-to-make-changes-to-film-near-hearing-at-high-court-on-this-date%2Farticleshow%2F113806790.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F113806790.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EThe%20Central%20Board%20of%20Film%20Certification%20(CBFC)%20has%20approved%20Kangana%