2%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-news%2Fgovernment-has-new-scam-alert-on-stock-trading-apps-and-platforms%2Farticleshow%2F113802878.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Moon's%20Temperature%20Dipped%20By%20Reduced%20Human%20Activity%20During%20Lockdown%3A%20Study%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20recent%20study%20by%20Indian%20researchers%20has%20revealed%20an%20unexpected%20consequence%20of%20the%20COVID-19%20lockdowns%3A%20a%20significant%20drop%20in%20lunar%20surface%20temperatures.%20During%20the%20global%20lockdown%20of%202020%2C%20the%20Moon's%20nighttime%20temperatures%20fell%20by%208-10%20Kelvin%2C%20suggesting%20a%20surprising%20connection%20between%20Earth's%20atmospheric%20changes%20and%20our%20celestial%20neighbour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnalyzing%20data%20from%20NASA's%20Lunar%20Reconnaissance%20Orbiter%2C%20researchers%20found%20that%20the%20temperature%20decrease%20coincided%20with%20a%20drastic%20reduction%20in%20human%20activities%20on%20Earth.%20The%20decline%20in%20greenhouse%20gas%20emissions%20and%20aerosols%20during%20the%20lockdown%20seems%20to%20have%20altered%20the%20radiation%20emitted%20from%20Earth%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20cooling%20effect%20on%20the%20Moon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20study%2C%20published%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2C%20noindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Facademic.oup.com%2Fmnrasl%2Farticle%2F535%2F1%2FL18%2F7760380%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EMonthly%20Notices%20of%20the%20Royal%20Astronomical%20Society%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20Letters%2C%20underscores%20the%20link%20between%20Earth%20and%20the%20Moon.%20As%20human%20activity%20resumed%20post-lockdown%2C%20lunar%20temperatures%20increased%2C%20suggesting%20that%20our%20actions%20may%20influence%20environments%20beyond%20Earth.%20Led%20by%20researchers%20K%20Durga%20Prasad%20and%20G%20Ambily%20from%20the%20Physical%20Research%20Laboratory%20(PRL)%2C%20the%20team%20analyzed%20lunar%20surface%20temperature%20data%20from%20six%20locations%20between%202017%20and%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnil%20Bharadwaj%2C%20director%20of%20PRL%2C%20emphasized%20the%20study's%20significance%20in%20exploring%20Earth's%20interaction%20with%20its%20closest%20celestial%20neighbour.%20The%20temperature%20drop%20in%202020%20offers%20a%20unique%20opportunity%20to%20examine%20how%20reduced%20human%20activity%20on%20Earth%20may%20have%20affected%20the%20Moon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20research%20shows%20that%20the%20decrease%20in%20human%20activity%20during%20the%20COVID-19%20lockdown%20impacted%20the%20Moon's%20temperatures%2C%20highlighting%20the%20interconnectedness%20of%20Earth%20and%20its%20celestial%20neighbour.%20This%20offers%20a%20fresh%20perspective%20on%20the%20broader%20cosmic%20effects%20of%20global%20human%20activity.%20While%20the%20findings%20present%20strong%20evidence%2C%20further%20data%20is%20needed%20to%20fully%20understand%20the%20Earth-Moon%20dynamic.%20Future%20lunar%20observatories%20could%20be%20key%20to%20advancing%20our%20understanding%20of%20how%20human%20actions%20influence%20the%20cosmos.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727673600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fl21mmi4o_super-moon_625x300_20_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fmoons-temperature-dipped-by-reduced-human-activity-on-earth-during-lockdown-study-6681416%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22This%20study%2C%20published%20in%20the%20Monthly%20Notices%20of%20the%20Royal%20Astronomical%20Society%3A%20Letters%2C%20underscores%20the%20link%20between%20Earth%20and%20the%20Moon.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fmoons-temperature-dipped-by-reduced-human-activity-on-earth-during-lockdown-study-6681416%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22After%20months%20of%20waiting%2C%20Gaza%20girls%20make%20it%20to%20It