ob%20at%20an%20edtech%20company%20in%202015%20to%20return%20to%20his%20ancestral%20property%2C%20where%20he%20would%20witness%20this%20plague%20and%20eventually%20start%20work%20towards%20finding%20a%20cure.%20The%20land%20that%20once%20hosted%20a%20brick%20factory%20had%2C%20by%202016%2C%20turned%20into%20a%20dump%20yard.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20first%20came%20here%2C%20the%20place%20was%20a%20big%20dump%20yard.%20Even%20the%20municipality%20staff%20came%20and%20dumped%20garbage%20here.%20It%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20very%20visible%20at%20first%20because%20of%20the%20trees%20surrounding%20the%20area%2C%E2%80%9D%20Utsow%20recalls.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20also%20thick%20undergrowth%20of%20plants.%20We%20didn%E2%80%99t%20really%20know%20the%20extent%20of%20the%20problem%20back%20then%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20time%20when%20development%20had%20almost%20become%20synonymous%20with%20concrete%20structures%2C%20Utsow%20decided%20to%20take%20a%20different%20route.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F359465%2Fsustainable-farming-homeschooling-rajesh-mate-smita-dhruvi-diti-mumbai-to-raigad-permaculture%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDrawing%20on%20tradition%20and%20his%20knowledge%20of%20permaculture%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20he%20founded%20%E2%80%98Tieedi%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20an%20acronym%20for%20%E2%80%98Take%20It%20Easy%2C%20Easy%20Does%20It%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMission%20Green%20Mile%3A%20A%20step%20towards%20sustainability%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CInitially%2C%20the%20goal%20was%20very%20personal%3B%20I%20wanted%20to%20explore%20natural%20buildings%20on%20my%20own%20and%20grow%20my%20own%20food.%20But%20when%20we%20started%20clearing%20the%20undergrowth%2C%20we%20began%20to%20experience%20firsthand%20the%20problem%20of%20plastic%20pollution%2C%E2%80%9D%20Utsow%20informs%20me%20as%20we%20sit%20in%20one%20of%20his%20mud