verything%20and%20everyone%2C%20no%20matter%20how%20far%2C%20feels%20close.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20burning%20desire%20to%20pursue%20her%20passion%20and%20share%20her%20art%20with%20the%20world%2C%20Varsha%20uploaded%20her%20first%20video.%20What%20began%20as%20short%20dance%20and%20comedy%20clips%20soon%20evolved%20into%20something%20bigger.%20But%20every%20coin%20has%20two%20sides.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20she%20faced%20harsh%20mockery%20and%20trolls%20hiding%20behind%20their%20screens%2C%20trying%20to%20pull%20her%20down.%20Varsha%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20one%20to%20give%20up%20easily.%20She%20flipped%20the%20coin%20%E2%80%94%20and%20her%20story.%20Her%20content%20began%20to%20gain%20traction%2C%20and%20soon%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F255612%2Fsocial-media-influencer-instagram-senior-citizens-mr-mrs-verma-yashpal-singh-shanta-jonita-haryana-trends-online-collaboration-romance-old-age-boredom-lockdown-inspirational-vid01%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eher%20videos%20began%20going%20viral%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPeople%20laughed%20at%20me%20at%20first%2C%E2%80%9D%20Varsha%20shared.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20then%20something%20incredible%20happened.%20My%20videos%20started%20to%20take%20off%2C%20and%20suddenly%2C%20people%20were%20following%20my%20journey.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20talent%20and%20charm%20earned%20her%20a%20spot%20on%20the%20popular%20dance%20reality%20show%20%3Cem%3EDance%20Deewane%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20where%20she%20wowed%20both%20the%20judges%20and%20the%20audience.%20One%20of%20the%20judges%20told%20her%2C%20%E2%80%9CYou%E2%80%99re%20a%20real%20hero.%20People%20need%20to%20learn%20from%20you.%20You%20didn%E2%80%99t%20let%20life%20drown%20you%20%E2%80%94%20you%20fought%20back.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20an%20emotional%20moment%20on%20the%20show%2C%20she%20reflected%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20used%20to%20dream%20about%20this%2C%20but%20never%20thought%20it%20could%20happen.%20Life%20has%20a%20funny%20way%20of%20giving%20you%20a%20second%20chance.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20with%205.8%20million%20followers%2C%20Varsha%20is%20living%20proof%20that%20an%20undying%20passion%20can%20take%20you%20to%20places%20you%20never%20even%20imagined.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Arunava%20Banerjee%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727446429000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D367863%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Born%20into%20poverty%2C%20Varsha%20Solanki%20worked%20as%20a%20domestic%20help%20while%20nurturing%20a%20lifelong%20passion%20for%20dance.%20After%20marriage%20and%20motherhood%2C%20she%20turned%20to%20social%20media%20to%20rekindle%20her%20art%2C%20going%20viral%20and%20reaching%20five%20million%20followers.%20Here's%20her%20story.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Khushi%20Arora%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A41%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F367863%2Fvarsha-solanki-social-media-sensation-reality-show-dance-deewane-story-watch-domestic-help-dancer-video%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Heart%20Attack%20Symptoms%20In%20Women%3A%20Spotting%20the%20Hidden%20Signs%20%26amp%3B%20How%20They%20Are%20Different%20For%20Women%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EHeart%20disease%20is%20commonly%20misconstrued%20as%20a%20problem%20associated%20primarily%20with%20men%2C%20but%20studies%20have%20shown%20that%20it%20is%20far%20from%20the%20truth.%20A%20lack%20of%20awareness%2C%20research%2C%20and%20prevention%20efforts%20has%20resulted%20in%20women%20often%20silently%20suffering%20from%2C%20and%20dying%20of%2C%20preventable%20heart%20diseases.%20This%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F317906%2Fhow-to-prevent-heart-attack-detect-cardiac-symptoms-ecg-device-sanketlife-rahul-neha-rastogi-noida%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWorld%20Heart%20Day%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20we%20aim%20to%20shift%20the%20narrative%20to%20the%20often-ignored%20subject%20of%20women%E2%80%99s%20heart%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELife%20was%20routine%20for%2040-year-old%20Neha%20until%20an%20incident%20shook%20her%20world.%20The%20Haridwar%20resident%20started%20experiencing%20sudden%20dizziness%20and%20fainting%20episodes%2C%20blacking%20out%20for%20a%20few%20seconds%20before%20regaining%20consciousness.%20This%20happened%20four%20to%20five%20times%20over%20two%20days.%20She%20visited%20a%20local%20doctor%20who%20advised%20her%20to%20immediately%20seek%20treatment%20from%20a%20specialist%20in%20Dehradun.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20conducting%20ECGs%20and%20other%20basic%20tests%2C%20the%20doctor%20in%20Dehradun%20realised%20that%20these%20were%20symptoms%20of%20sudden%20cardiac%20arrests%20and%20referred%20her%20to%20the%20Fortis%20Escorts%20Heart%20Institute%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20where%20she%20proceeded%20for%20treatment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Aparna%20Jaswal%2C%20Director%20of%20Cardiology%2C%20Department%20of%20Cardiac%20Pacing%20and%20Electrophysiology%20at%20Fortis%2C%20identified%20Neha%E2%80%99s%20symptoms%20as%20a%20heart%20ailment%2C%20explaining%20that%20her%20sudden%20fainting%20episodes%20were%20the%20result%20of%20cardiac%20arrest.%20They%20were%20able%20to%20identify%20the%20ailment%20through%20continuous%20heart%20monitoring.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeha%E2%80%99s%20case%20is%20not%20the%20only%20one.%20The%20prevalence%20of%20coronary%20artery%20diseases%20in%20women%20range%20from%20three%20to%2013%20percent%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3EJournal%20of%20the%20American%20College%20of%20Cardiology%3C%2Fem%3E.%20The%20report%20also%20states%20that%20the%20disease%20has%20increased%20by%20over%20300%20percent%20in%20the%20past%2020%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Global%20Burden%20of%20Disease%20Study%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F341755%2Fcongenital-heart-disease-in-babies-treatment-surgery-provided-by-hans-foundation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eheart%20disease%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20leading%20cause%20of%20fatality%20among%20Indian%20women%2C%20accounting%20for%20over%2017%20percent%20of%20deaths.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20alarming%20statistic%20underscores%20the%20importance%20of%20recognising%20the%20unique%20ways%20heart%20diseases%20manifest%20in%20women%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20critical%20need%20for%20awareness%20and%20proactive%20health%20management.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHeart%20disease%20is%20the%20biggest%20killer%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHeart%20disease%20refers%20to%20a%20range%20of%20conditions%20like%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F336492%2Fgoan-artist-xavier-fernandes-makes-christmas-cribs-from-driftwood%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecoronary%20artery%20disease%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20congenital%20heart%20disease%2C%20arrhythmia%20(irregular%20heartbeats)%2C%20cardiac%20arrest%2C%20and%20more.%20It%20is%20one%20of%20the%20leading%20causes%20of%20death%20worldwide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20more%20often%20than%20not%2C%20heart%20diseases%20are%20preventable%20and%20can%20be%20successfully%20treated%20if%20diagnosed%20early.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20traditional%20belief%20is%20that%20heart%20diseases%20generally%20affect%20women%2010%20years%20later%20than%20men%2C%20this%20is%20no%20longer%20the%20case.%20Just%20like%20younger%20men%20are%20getting%20heart%20attacks%2C%20so%20are%20women%2C%20but%20they%20are%20often%20unaware%20of%20the%20signs%20and%20symptoms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuplo