minutes%20or%20recurs%2C%20Dr%20Rao%20informs.%20However%2C%20he%20adds%20that%20chest%20pain%20experienced%20by%20women%20may%20differ%20slightly%20from%20that%20experienced%20by%20men%2C%20often%20described%20more%20as%20pressure%20or%20tightness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COther%20symptoms%20seen%20in%20women%20include%20neck%2C%20jaw%20and%20shoulder%20pain%2C%20shortness%20of%20breath%2C%20pain%20in%20one%20or%20both%20arms%2C%20nausea%20or%20vomiting%2C%20sweating%2C%20or%20dizziness.%20Women%20should%20be%20particularly%20cautious%20about%20atypical%20symptoms%2C%20as%20they%20may%20not%20be%20recognised%20as%20signs%20of%20a%20heart%20attack%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Jaswal%20adds%20that%20dizziness%2C%20blurring%20or%20fainting%2C%20radiating%20pain%20to%20the%20shoulders%20and%20jaw%2C%20extreme%20fatigue%20or%20breathlessness%2C%20and%20palpitations%20are%20also%20symptoms%20seen%20in%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FCopy-of-Infographic-website-3-1727414804.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FCopy-of-Infographic-website-3-1727414804.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FCopy-of-Infographic-website-3-1727414804-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FCopy-of-Infographic-website-3-1727414804-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FCopy-of-Infographic-website-3-1727414804-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FCopy-of-Infographic-website-3-1727414804-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-367765%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E(Symptoms%20from%20the%20World%20Heart%20Federation)%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20informs%20that%20earlier%2C%20hormones%20were%20believed%20to%20provide%20protection%20against%20heart%20diseases%20till%20menopause%2C%20when%20the%20levels%20dropped.%20However%2C%20that%20is%20not%20the%20case%20today%2C%20as%20younger%20women%2C%20too%2C%20experience%20heart%20ailments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERisk%20factors%20include%20high%20blood%20pressure%2C%20high%20cholesterol%2C%20diabetes%2C%20smoking%2C%20and%20a%20family%20history%20of%20heart%20disease.%20If%20you%20have%20any%20of%20these%2C%20you%20should%20get%20regular%20check-ups.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEvery%20adult%2C%20be%20it%20a%20woman%20or%20a%20man%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F288854%2Ftamil-nadu-auto-driver-daughter-tops-board-exams-after-fathers-heart-attack%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emust%20get%20yearly%20check-ups%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Check%20your%20blood%20pressure%20and%20sugar%2C%20especially%20if%20you%20have%20a%20family%20history%20of%20heart%20disease.%20If%20any%20of%20these%20levels%20are%20elevated%2C%20treat%20them%20on%20time.%20Heart%20diseases%20are%20preventable%20if%20these%20risk%20factors%20are%20in%20check%20and%20monitored%20regularly%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dr%20Jaswal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditional%20risk%20factors%20for%20women%20include%20pregnancy%20complications.%20If%20a%20woman%20has%20gestational%20diabetes%20or%20preeclampsia%20(high%20blood%20pressure)%2C%20the%20risk%20of%20heart%20disease%20later%20increases.%20Therefore%2C%20doctors%20stress%20that%20it%20is%20vital%20for%20women%20of%20all%20ages%20to%20prioritise%20their%20heart%20health.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20World%20Heart%20Federation%2C%20women%20also%20tend%20to%20have%20more%20severe%20first%20heart%20attacks%20that%20more%20frequently%20lead%20to%20death%20compared%20to%20men.%20%E2%80%9CWomen%20are%20the%20forefront%20and%20backbone%20of%20the%20family.%20Yet%2C%20they%20quietly%20die%20due%20to%20sudden%20cardiac%20arrests%2C%20and%20not%20much%20is%20spoken%20about%20it.%20It%E2%80%99s%20time%20that%20women%20recognise%20the%20warning%20signs%20and%20rush%20to%20the%20hospital%20any%20time%20they%20experience%20any%20of%20the%20symptoms%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Jaswal%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20urges%20women%20to%20have%20yearly%20health%20check-ups%20and%20take%20immediate%20action%20if%20any%20of%20their%20levels%20are%20high.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeha%E2%80%99s%20prompt%20thinking%20probably%20saved%20her%20life.%20You%20too%20can%20save%20yours%20by%20taking%20care%20of%20your%20health%20and%20acting%20promptly.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTime%20is%20critical%20during%20a%20heart%20attack%2C%20and%20even%20a%20minute%20can%20turn%20the%20situation%20around%20for%20a%C2%A0%20person.%20In%20crucial%20times%2C%20you%20should%20trust%20your%20instincts%2C%20and%20if%20something%20feels%20wrong%2C%20you%20should%20immediately%20seek%20medical%20attention%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dr%20Rao.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Arunava%20Banerjee%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727419891000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fheart-care-1040227_1280-1727414916.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D367755%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Heart%20disease%20manifests%20differently%20in%20women%20and%20is%20an%20oft%20ignored%20subject.%20We%20spoke%20to%20doctors%20who%20explained%20the%20different%20symptoms%20women%20experience%20and%20the%20warning%20signs%20that%20must%20not%20be%20ignored.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F367755%2Fworld-heart-day-heart-disease-heart-attack-w