ng%20more%20men%20involved%20in%20contraception%20and%20family%20planning%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20how%20do%20we%20get%20more%20men%20involved%20in%20contraception%20and%20family%20planning%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThus%20far%2C%20the%20Union%20Ministry%20of%20Health%20and%20Family%20Welfare%20has%20taken%20some%20steps%20to%20mainstream%20men%E2%80%99s%20role%20in%20family%20planning.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Poonam%2C%20these%20include%2C%20%E2%80%9CVasectomy%20fortnight%20(every%20November)%2C%20installation%20of%20condom%20boxes%20at%20all%20levels%20of%20health%20care%20facilities%2C%20IIC%2FBCC%20campaigns%20to%20promote%20male%20contraceptives%2C%20counselling%20of%20men%20on%20contraceptives%20by%20involvement%20of%20ASHAs%2C%20distribution%20of%20Nayi%20Pehel%20kit%20containing%20condoms%20for%20newlyweds%2C%20and%20organisation%20of%20the%20Saas%20Bahu%20Pati%20Sammelan%20to%20promote%20male%20engagement%20under%20Mission%20Parivar%20Vikas%20programme.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20initiatives%20have%20increased%20awareness%20and%20demand%20for%20family%20planning.%20But%20there%20is%20much%20more%20to%20be%20achieved%20to%20realise%20gender%20equity%20fully%20and%20shared%20responsibility%20in%20family%20planning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FVasectomy-4-1727272091.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Vasectomy%20for%20Indian%20family%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FVasectomy-4-1727272091.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FVasectomy-4-1727272091-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FVasectomy-4-1727272091-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FVasectomy-4-1727272091-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FVasectomy-4-1727272091-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-367532%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ERepresentational%20Image%3A%20%E2%80%9CBy%20engaging%20men%20as%20equal%20partners%20in%20family%20planning%2C%20we%20may%20unlock%20a%20critical%20pathway%20to%20driving%20meaningful%20change%20in%20the%20country.%E2%80%9D%20(Image%20courtesy%20Shutterstock%2FMaster%20of%20Stocks)%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAddressing%20stereotypes%20and%20encouraging%20men%20to%20view%20family%20planning%20as%20a%20shared%20responsibility%20requires%20a%20comprehensive%20approach.%20Public%20health%20systems%2C%20family%20planning%20programmes%2C%20and%20communication%20strategies%20must%20be%20tailored%20to%20promote%20male%20involvement%20actively.%20By%20engaging%20men%20as%20equal%20partners%20in%20family%20planning%2C%20we%20may%20unlock%20a%20critical%20pathway%20to%20driving%20meaningful%20change%20in%20the%20country%2C%E2%80%9D%20argues%20Poonam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20sustained%20effort%20in%20behaviour%20change%20communication%2C%20combined%20with%20active%20on-ground%20engagement%20with%20men%2C%20is%20essential%20while%20promoting%20women%E2%80%99s%20rights%20and%20decision-making%20autonomy.%20The%20focus%20should%20be%20on%20shifting%20mindsets%20and%20addressing%20stereotypes%20to%20empower%20women%20in%20making%20informed%20health%20decisions%2C%20while%20also%20fostering%20open%20communication%20between%20spouses.%20It%E2%80%99s%20crucial%20to%20initiate%20these%20efforts%20early%20by%20engaging%20adolescents%20in%20discussions%20about%20sexual%20and%20reproductive%20health%20and%20rights.%20Additionally%2C%20strategic%20engagement%20is%20needed%20to%20encourage%20men%20to%20consider%20vasectomy%20as%20a%20viable%20family%20planning%20option%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20do%20we%20get%20there%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPoonam%20notes%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20important%20to%20understand%20that%20male%20engagement%20intervention%20needs%20a%20multi-sectoral%20approach.%20Education%2C%20age%20at%20marriage%2C%20health-seeking%20behaviour%2C%20and%20socio-cultural%20norms%20need%20to%20be%20addressed%20simultaneously%20and%20concurrently.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20two%20steps%20she%20recommends%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EFrontline%20health%20workers%20(ASHAs%2C%20ANMs)%20must%20be%20supported%20and%20male%20health%20workers%20must%20be%20added%20to%20supplement%20the%20existing%20workforce.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EGiven%20the%20Government%E2%80%99s%20present%20emphasis%20on%20strengthening%20counselling%20at%20hospitals%2C%20an%20increased%20thrust%20on%20couples%20counselling%20and%20follow-ups%20is%20likely%20to%20bear%20fruit.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FVasectomy-5-1727272212.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22What%20is%20the%20right%20solution%20for%20couples%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FVasectomy-5-1727272212.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FVasectomy-5-1727272212-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FVasectomy-5-1727272212-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FVasectomy-5-1727272212-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FVasectomy-5-1727272212-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-367538%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ERepresentational%20Image%20courtesy%20Shutterstock%2FIndianFaces%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Government%E2%80%99s%20effort%20to%20engage%20male%20peer%20educators%20as%20part%20of%20the%20RKSK%20(Rashtriya%20Kishor%20Swasthya%20Karyakram)%20programme%20is%20a%20move%20in%20the%20right%20direction%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLastly%2C%20the%20involvement%20of%20other%20stakeholders%2C%20including%20civil%20society%20organisations%20and%20private%20partners%2C%20to%20involve%20men%20in%20this%20process%20needs%20to%20be%20underlined.%20Innovative%20ways%20to%20ensure%20this%20under%20existing%20PPP%20(public-private%20partnership)%20and%20social%20franchising%20models%20will%20positively%20impact%20health%20and%20family%20planning%20at%20the%20community%20level%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhy%20is%20male%20participation%20crucial%20in%20family%20planning%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajesh%20believes%20that%20if%20you%20already%20have%20a%20child%20and%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20intend%20to%20have%20another%2C%20getting%20a%20vasectomy%20is%20a%20must%20so%20that%20you%20can%20move%20on%20in%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20have%20decided%20not%20to%20have%20children%20at%20all%2C%20my%20suggestion%20is%20to%20take%2018%20months%20as%20a%20couple%20to%20discuss%20this%20in%20honest%20detail%2C%20do%20the%20research%2C%20talk%20to%20experts%2C%20understand%20what%20it%20is%20to%20be%20a%20parent%20and%20have%20those%20delicate%20conversations%20with%20your%20family.%20Once%20you%20are%20clear%20about%20this%20decision%2C%20get%20the%20procedure%20done%20and%20move%20on%20ahead%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20argues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20said%20that%2C%20Poonam%20notes%20that%20the%20discourse%20on%20the%20engagement%20of%20men%20as%20partners%20in%20accessing%20family%20planning%20and%20health%20services%20needs%20to%20go%20beyond%20contraceptive%20use.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMale%20participation%20is%20about%20being%20responsible%20and%20respecting%20equality%20rather%20than%20just%20about%20decision-making.%20It%20should%20extend%20to%20the%20role%20of%20men%20as%20enablers%20and%20beneficiaries%20in%20the%20process%20of%20ensuring%20dignity%2C%20equal%20voice%2C%20and%20reproductive%20rights%20for%20women.%20Male%20participation%20should%20not%20mean%20that%20women%E2%80%99s%20decision-making%20powers%20are%20encumbered%2C%20and%20women%20are%20forced%20to%20accept%20men%E2%80%99s%20choices%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20argues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CStudies%20reveal%20that%20men%20often%20control%20contraception%20decision-making%20and%20decision%20of%20contraception%20of%20female%20partners%2C%20particularly%20in%20the%20context%20of%20the%20prevalence%20of%20intimate%20partner%20violence%2C%20which%20can%20impede%20contraceptive%20use%20as%20well%20as%20increase%20the%20risk%20for%20contraceptive%20failure.%20Male%20engagement%20in%20family%20planning%20should%20improve%20men%E2%80%99s%20and%20women%E2%80%99s%20reproductive%20health%20and%20promote%20gender%20equality%20and%20women%E2%80%99s%20empowerment%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20Images%20courtesy%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.shutterstock.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EShutterstock%3C%2Fa%3E)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727275238000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FVasectomy-2-1727271677.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D367509%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20Mumbai-based%20couple%20chose%20a%20vasectomy%20after%20deciding%20not%20to%20have%20children%2C%20breaking%20societal%20norms.%20Their%20decision%20came%20after%20extensive%20discussions%2C%20research%2C%20and%20consultations%20with%20doctors.%20Highlighting%20the%20simplicity%20of%20the%20procedure%20and%20societal%20challenges%2C%20they%20advocate%20for%20more%20men%20to%20take%20responsibility%20for%20family%20planning%20in%20India.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Rinchen%20Norbu%20Wangchuk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F367509%2Fworld-contraception-day-why-more-indian-men-should-get-vasectomy-family-planning%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Be%20Kind%E2%80%99%3A%20What%20Toxic%20Workplaces%20Can%20Learn%20From%20Companies%20Building%20Healthy%20Environments%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20hope%20my%20child%E2%80%99s%20experience%20leads%20to%20real%20change%20so%20that%20no%20other%20family%20has%20to%20endure%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F265281%2Frajani-jagtap-mumbai-doctor-online-grief-counselling%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egrief%20and%20trauma%3C%2Fa%3E%20we%20are%20going%20through.%20My%20Anna%20is%20no%20longer%20with%20us%2C%20but%20her%20story%20can%20still%20make%20a%20difference%2C%E2%80%9D%20wrote%20Anita%20Augustine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20heart-wrenching%20words%20come%20from%20a%20mother%20grieving%20the%20loss%20of%20her%20daughter%2C%20Anna%20Sebastian%20Perayil%2C%20who%20passed%20away%20in%20July%202024.%20A%20chartered%20accountant%20at%20EY%20(Ernst%20%26amp%3B%20Young)%20India%2C%20Anna%E2%80%99s%20mother%20claims%20her%20death%20was%20caused%20by%20overwhelming%20work%20pressure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnna%20had%20only%20begun%20her%20career%20at%20the%20firm%20in%20March%202024%2C%20but%20according%20to%20her%20family%20and%20colleagues%2C%20she%20was%20quickly%20burdened%20with%20excessive%20work.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20workload%2C%20new%20environment%2C%20and%20long%20hours%20took%20a%20toll%20on%20her%20physically%2C%20mentally%20and%20emotionally.%20She%20began%20experiencing%20anxiety%2C%20sleeplessness%2C%20and%20stress%20but%20kept%20pushing%20herself%2C%20believing%20that%20hard%20work%20and%20perseverance%20were%20the%20keys%20to%20success%2C%E2%80%9D%20Anita%20added%20in%20the%20letter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tragic%20death%20of%2026-year-old%20Anna%20has%20cast%20a%20spotlight%20on%20the%20critical%20importance%20of%20fostering%20a%20healthy%20work%20culture%20and%20implementing%20policies%20that%20promote%20a%20supportive%20environment.%20Anna%E2%80%99s%20story%20is%20not%20an%20isolated%20case%2C%20as%20the%20flood%20of%20grief%20and%20anger%20on%20social%20media%20reveals.%20Many%20people%20have%20come%20forward%2C%20sharing%20their%20own%20experiences%20with%20toxic%20workplaces%2C%20the%20stress%20they%20endured%2C%20and%20how%20it%20led%20to%20health%20issues%20or%20even%20forced%20them%20to%20quit%20their%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%2C%20the%20National%20Human%20Rights%20Commission%20(NHRC)%20has%20issued%20a%20notice%20to%20the%20Union%20Ministry%20of%20Labour%20and%20Employment%2C%20requesting%20details%20about%20the%20investigation%E2%80%99s%20findings%20and%20the%20measures%20being%20taken%20to%20prevent%20further%20loss%20of%20young%20lives%20due%20to%20work-related%20stress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6.%20chasing%20impractical%20targets%20and%20timelines%20is%20resulting%20in%20grave%20violations%20of%20human%20rights%20of%20the%20employees.%20It%20is%20the%20prime%20duty%20of%20every%20employer%20to%20provide%20a%20safe%2C%20secure%20and%20positive%20environment%20to%20its%20employees.%20They%20must%20ensure%20that%20everyone%20working%20with%20them%20is%20treated%20with%20dignity%20and%20fairness%2C%E2%80%9D%20wrote%20the%20NHRC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20can%20companies%20create%20better%20workplaces%20where%20employees%20can%20truly%20thrive%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20explore%20this%2C%20we%20spoke%20with%20employees%20from%20organisations%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F331893%2Fmental-health-care-therapy-counselling-affordable-startups-india-online%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprioritise%20wellbeing%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20HR%20experts%20who%20design%20employee-friendly%20policies%2C%20employers%20who%20champion%20flexible%20work%20cultures%2C%20and%20mental%20health%20organisations%20that%20collaborate%20with%20companies%20to%20foster%20overall%20wellness.%20Their%20insights%20provide%20valuable%20answers%20to%20building%20healthier%2C%20more%20supportive%20workplaces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ECompanies%20that%20walk%20the%20talk%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20us%20dedicate%20our%20lives%20to%20work%2C%20often%20without%20realising%20that%20we%E2%80%99re%20missing%20out%20on%20precious%20time%20with%20family%2C%20friends%2C%20and%20most%20importantly%2C%20ourselves.%20Roshne%20Balasubramanian%20%E2%80%94%20a%20former%20journalist%20and%20now%20senior%20manager%20of%20communications%20at%20the%20Nalandaway%20Foundation%2C%20a%20non-profit%20organisation%20%E2%80%94%20admits%20to%20having%20done%20the%20same%20in%20her%20previous%20roles.%20She%20worked%20in%20toxic%20environments%20that%20took%20a%20toll%20on%20both%20her%20mental%20and%20physical%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20when%20her%20mother%20fell%20ill%2C%20Roshne%20was%20forced%20to%20reassess%20her%20priorities%2C%20ultimately%20leaving%20journalism.%20She%20describes%20Nalandaway%20as%20a%20refreshing%20change%2C%20where%20employee%20well-being%20is%20truly%20valued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FCopy-of-Infographic-website-2-1727184704.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22How%20can%20companies%20build%20a%20healthy%20workplace%3F%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FCopy-of-Infographic-website-2-1727184704.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FCopy-of-Infographic-website-2-1727184704-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FCopy-of-Infographic-website-2-1727184704-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FCopy-of-Infographic-website-2-1727184704-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FCopy-of-Infographic-website-2-1727184704-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-367335%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20company%20not%20just%20talks%20the%20talk%2C%20but%20also%20walks%20the%20walk.%20It%20feels%20good%20to%20be%20part%20of%20a%20workspace%20that%20is%20accommodative%20and%20understanding.%20Due%20to%20my%20mother%E2%80%99s%20illness%2C%20I%20had%20to%20work%20from%20home%20for%20some%20time%2C%20which%20I%20was%20initially%20hesitant%20to%20ask%20for%2C%20but%20they%20made%20it%20happen%20for%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Roshne.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20organisation%20offers%20a%20comprehensive%20employee%20wellness%20programme%2C%20which%20includes%20reimbursements%20for%20therapy%20sessions%2C%2010%20paid%20period%20leaves%20annually%2C%20and%20a%20monthly%20team%20bonding%20activity%20called%20Thursday%20Circles%2C%20where%20employees%20come%20together%20to%20share%20personal%20stories.%20They%20also%20host%20%E2%80%98Brews%20%26amp%3B%20Banter%E2%80%99%2C%20a%20bi-monthly%20engagement%20activity%20aimed%20at%20fostering%20connection%20among%20staff.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20Nalandaway%20has%20an%20open%20forum%20grievance%20redressal%20policy%2C%20ensuring%20employees%20have%20a%20safe%20space%20to%20voice%20concerns