areer%2C%20Kadam%20approached%20a%20director%20for%20a%20Doordarshan%20role%20but%20was%20told%20the%20casting%20was%20done%20and%20was%20offered%20an%20assistant%20position%20instead.%20She%20accepted%2C%20but%20when%20the%20lead%20actor%20didn%E2%80%99t%20show%20up%2C%20Kadam%20was%20offered%20the%20part.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20one%20of%20those%20moments%20where%20I%20knew%20I%20was%20at%20the%20right%20place%20at%20the%20right%20time.%20What%E2%80%99s%20meant%20for%20you%20will%20find%20its%20way%20to%20you%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalled.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20victories%2C%20Kadam%20often%20found%20herself%20doubting%20whether%20she%20even%20%E2%80%9Clooked%20like%20an%20actress%E2%80%9D.%20In%20an%20industry%20where%20looks%2C%20contacts%2C%20and%20fluency%20in%20English%20often%20determined%20success%2C%20Kadam%2C%20who%20was%20not%20formally%20trained%2C%20felt%20out%20of%20place.%20%E2%80%9CI%20started%20doing%20parts%20for%20Rs%20250%20a%20day.%20Everyone%20around%20me%20seemed%20younger%2C%20smarter%2C%20and%20more%20connected%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20reflected.%20But%20she%20refused%20to%20let%20any%20limitations%20define%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20breakthrough%20came%20in%202013%20with%20%3Cem%3EFandry%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20where%20her%20powerful%20portrayal%20of%20Naani%2C%20a%20woman%20battling%20caste%20oppression%2C%20earned%20her%20critical%20acclaim.%20Following%20this%2C%20she%20played%20a%20string%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F258142%2Fdilip-kumar-tribute-shah-rukh-khan-amitabh-bachchan-mughal-e-azam-bollywood%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eunforgettable%20roles%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Marathi%20films%20like%20%3Cem%3ESairat%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3ENude%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20which%20further%20solidified%20her%20presence%20in%20the%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20Kadam%20took%20on%20a%20notable%20role%20in%20Sriram%20Raghavan%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3EAndhadhun%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20in%202022%2C%20she%20starred%20alongside%20Amitabh%20Bachchan%20in%20%3Cem%3EJhund%3C%2Fem%3E%20as%20Ranjana%2C%20the%20wife%20of%20Bachchan%E2%80%99s%20character.%20She%20credits%20this%20milestone%20to%20her%20portrayal%20of%20the%20invisible%20women%20she%20has%20championed%20on%20screen%20without%20a%20second%20thought%20throughout%20her%20career.%20%E2%80%9CI%20never%20thought%20about%20playing%20one%20character%20and%20not%20another%3B%20I%20just%20followed%20my%20heart%20and%20played%20what%20I%20wanted%20to%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20this%20same%20pursuit%20of%20her%20inner%20voice%20that%20first%20led%20her%20to%20the%20acting%20workshop%20in%202001.%20In%20May%20this%20year%2C%2023%20years%20since%20that%20day%2C%20Kadam%20graced%20the%20screens%20at%20the%20Festival%20de%20Cannes%20not%20once%2C%20but%20twice%20%E2%80%94%20with%20Payal%20Kapadia%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3EAll%20We%20Imagine%20as%20Light%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20won%20the%20Grand%20Prix%20award%2C%20and%20Karan%20Kandhari%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3ESister%20Midnight.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20she%20continues%20to%20break%20barriers%20in%20an%20industry%20that%20once%20questioned%20her%2C%20Kadam%20refuses%20to%20slow%20down%20just%20yet.%20%E2%80%9CI%20admit%20that%20I%20may%20have%20to%20work%20harder%20than%20some%20others%20to%20achieve%20what%20I%20want%2C%20but%20I%20am%20ready%20to%20do%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Arunava%20Banerjee%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESources%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theestablished.com%2Fculture%2Fentertainment%2Flaapataa-ladies-chhaya-kadams-bollywood-journey-from-earning-rs-250-a-day-to-the-cannes-red-carpet%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELaapataa%